"{\"event\":\"job.completed\",\"jobId\":\"a9d56915-9a89-4834-b05a-93cc5c9176bd\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-23T07:38:32.928Z\",\"status\":\"completed\",\"result\":{\"data\":[\"v0.2\",{\"title\":\"Comment analysis\",\"description\":\"Analysis of comments\",\"topics\":[{\"id\":\"f26e239b-989e-4986-a00c-26040d030cfe\",\"title\":\"AI Impact and Concerns\",\"description\":\"AI Impact and Concerns\",\"summary\":\"The discussion on 'AI Impact and Concerns' highlights varied perspectives on AI's social, ethical, and positive implications. Key concerns include AI diminishing human empathy, personal interaction, and contributing to bullying via social media. Ethical issues arise around privacy, authentic content creation, and algorithm-driven categorization limiting freedom. Despite these concerns, there are positive applications, notably in healthcare, where AI revolutionizes diagnostics and treatment, and mental health by predicting episodes. Advocates stress the importance of incorporating AI education in schools to foster responsible use, while improvements in employment prospects through AI-assisted resume crafting are noted. Overall, the dialogue reflects tension between AI's potential benefits and risks, calling for balanced development and deployment.\",\"subtopics\":[{\"id\":\"925e16b7-97bf-4431-9723-c7df4d3e2c76\",\"title\":\"Social and Cultural Effects\",\"description\":\"Social and Cultural Effects\",\"claims\":[{\"id\":\"f8ac1ef6-7291-4e6c-bfab-c1c18016ac43\",\"title\":\"AI use threatens to reduce human empathy and compassion\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"2cf2d875-6e65-4c57-ac29-ac0034a14a9e\",\"text\":\"AI can't be expected to have compassion.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"fd10fa01-b0de-451e-be53-2c32589b36e4\",\"sourceId\":\"ca243b1a-dcc2-4daf-b207-ec94b8998efa\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":28,\"endIdx\":68}]}}],\"number\":1,\"similarClaims\":[{\"id\":\"3e379d98-71ac-4807-97b3-4ed7215772ae\",\"title\":\"AI use may reduce human empathy and compassion.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"93f1b3a4-df71-4e74-a447-a01b837bdc41\",\"text\":\"[...] that is what's really missing and that is a pity on all of society and that's your compassion because how do you have compassion if you haven't talked to someone else [...]\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"b2cfe25e-92cd-4c3e-b884-2068a73762de\",\"sourceId\":\"f4a31078-1100-4797-8b71-e826145f8666\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":-1,\"endIdx\":177}]}}],\"number\":2,\"similarClaims\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"a770f927-ddcf-47e7-9f8c-0a6c083a882f\",\"title\":\"AI should not replace human interaction and expression\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"26c3d525-8191-4640-80c2-f558c56bd10c\",\"text\":\"I don't want to see it replacing humans writing because writing is a wonderful skill and it's something I really enjoy.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"098b9b89-135b-4ac4-a239-5ec3016e9c52\",\"sourceId\":\"f12d5863-e0c0-4488-a31b-a9f1a9bee26e\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":35,\"endIdx\":154}]}}],\"number\":3,\"similarClaims\":[{\"id\":\"6e0304f0-cc8c-410c-975f-8f5343a644ab\",\"title\":\"AI should not replace human interaction.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"5a1df396-bb69-4a34-a8a4-76f270ebbcfb\",\"text\":\"we, I think we have to hold on to our humanity in the face of this.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"6dcee7a9-f661-49af-843d-a9bd4530ac81\",\"sourceId\":\"9fa5a3a4-ca60-4b7c-961b-b450c85348e4\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":150,\"endIdx\":217}]}}],\"number\":4,\"similarClaims\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"7e765e28-4c66-4702-a0c3-a44613420942\",\"title\":\"AI reduces personal interaction and contributes to a decline of face-to-face communication\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"bd09031e-61be-444f-9ad6-6bd16e82b290\",\"text\":\"with them just learning through machines, you're not getting that personal human touch.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"797ba6fe-423d-42a8-b47a-81c60e823456\",\"sourceId\":\"a8b0b2cf-d3bb-44a3-9e73-65ecb0f74b27\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":135,\"endIdx\":222}]}}],\"number\":5,\"similarClaims\":[{\"id\":\"6a3d597d-7c96-4544-99f6-c7d2583f9019\",\"title\":\"AI contributes to the decline of face-to-face interaction in society.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"3f415963-fc9c-476f-bd25-a8d35fe8b77a\",\"text\":\"Oh. They're texting or they're playing a game.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"7799829c-399e-4ef3-9a55-c97e1699159f\",\"sourceId\":\"0cd41323-b0ec-42cc-9eb7-9e77726c49a4\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":88,\"endIdx\":134}]}}],\"number\":6,\"similarClaims\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"0d9ef9e6-048c-4812-a2d7-ab3b88956458\",\"title\":\"AI and social media contribute to bullying and peer pressure among youth\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"52271905-27d3-4e95-a697-3d98ff8d42e4\",\"text\":\"That's very scary to me now with social media, they say such cruel things, and I have a granddaughter who in 8th grade kind of got in the mean girl thing [...]\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"c1776522-58ad-4e8f-9764-f8bbfa4b9fda\",\"sourceId\":\"636d605c-1716-43f0-a0c7-a9aeac1266ec\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":-1,\"endIdx\":158}]}}],\"number\":7,\"similarClaims\":[{\"id\":\"bec1d4fc-b895-40cc-9885-e68ce96d1030\",\"title\":\"AI contributes to dehumanization and increase in bullying.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"023dcc9c-27d6-48bd-91f7-2f201727b9c1\",\"text\":\"And, and it really, it's, it's scary that bullying in schools is going on to the extent that it is. [...] this isn't a person, this isn't two eyes looking at you [...] but if I can do it on this phone.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"fd7449ee-adb3-4fbe-9a2f-a5bebcdaf814\",\"sourceId\":\"1ab7e84b-20c6-4c77-878c-53a4fb5f19dd\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":-1,\"endIdx\":200}]}}],\"number\":8,\"similarClaims\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"b42e66ff-95bf-425b-929f-2be22408e395\",\"title\":\"Education should focus on enhancing human skills and critical thinking in an AI-driven world\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"418abd96-0ae5-4782-a557-d0741f6da932\",\"text\":\"Where does critical thinking come into that, though? I mean, to teach kids to think apart from AI or how to channel AI.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"3afe4f21-e0c6-4dc3-a86c-6e3caf22d80f\",\"sourceId\":\"17306c3a-3cdc-4105-9ba8-50f09fad23a4\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":0,\"endIdx\":119}]}}],\"number\":9,\"similarClaims\":[{\"id\":\"a6045d39-6863-428e-9575-4083b87c2d94\",\"title\":\"Human skills should be enhanced to balance AI advancements.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"7a6d0e45-bf3e-4d0c-bb65-ff208091516f\",\"text\":\"Rather than trying to limit AI, maybe we need to kind of up our human game to balance it, right?\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"009028b0-40fb-49e5-9afd-c0fb438ded8c\",\"sourceId\":\"927b2912-c210-4fdb-b53b-aba4d2b75eba\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":42,\"endIdx\":138}]}}],\"number\":10,\"similarClaims\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"d810c5b7-4920-42db-8854-5d9cab8ef4ed\",\"title\":\"AI creates echo chambers that reinforce existing beliefs\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"3686ce03-eaab-4983-9a13-c27163b3359d\",\"text\":\"[...] when they're siloed up in these AI chambers, and they're just getting hearing more and more of those algorithms, feeding them more what they wanna hear.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"272942b6-2dd8-405f-8cb8-917744f6d1ac\",\"sourceId\":\"0215d702-ec95-4801-96b7-46079de3a549\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":-1,\"endIdx\":157}]}}],\"number\":11,\"similarClaims\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"74e70fd7-dc33-46b9-86ec-791b4266306f\",\"title\":\"Ethical and Privacy Issues\",\"description\":\"Ethical and Privacy Issues\",\"claims\":[{\"id\":\"6a6c32fd-76ff-4e5b-b001-61f70279c15b\",\"title\":\"AI's role in content creation raises concerns about authenticity, copyright, and accurate attribution.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"1cad04f8-928b-4e3f-bb37-b7e1cc48236f\",\"text\":\"there's so much there that's controlling stuff. If you go on Facebook or YouTube [...] including fabricated pictures.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"612d40ad-de37-4a6a-8d6c-e2c1dea1c005\",\"sourceId\":\"f2f10fc5-c4bb-4bc4-84f4-ab262bcdb314\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":-1,\"endIdx\":116}]}}],\"number\":12,\"similarClaims\":[{\"id\":\"f784c377-5b57-49db-a807-c10af44ea698\",\"title\":\"AI tools can create content indistinguishable from real, raising copyright and attribution concerns.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"1d6f03ec-39ed-4e95-913d-e3cf81bcfb17\",\"text\":\"You can't even tell if they're real anymore, you know, there's no copyright. There's no credits, there's no nothing.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"e81811f8-7bdf-4d03-86a7-ff808c7aa9fe\",\"sourceId\":\"08d81ee2-fc32-4eda-9d35-d9016a9431cf\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":-1,\"endIdx\":115}]}}],\"number\":13,\"similarClaims\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"5e974d75-f1fb-4052-a7f3-bcb5134bf4c4\",\"title\":\"AI development and deployment by unknown creators pose potential safety risks.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"f21a883f-015a-437a-b7bb-25b8cf39d7a9\",\"text\":\"I picture, uh, you know, some 19 year old guy living in his mother's basement or something, you know, doing all this stuff, and, you know, I really don't know what it is, but to me it's just scary as hell what could happen.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"4efb9c25-a28d-4fc4-9e2c-3788f29b58d4\",\"sourceId\":\"08d81ee2-fc32-4eda-9d35-d9016a9431cf\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":156,\"endIdx\":379}]}}],\"number\":14,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"59d07726-82e8-4d60-a998-c9970e7bc1c3\",\"title\":\"AI technologies listening constantly heighten privacy concerns.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"2a7d25f2-7616-48b5-8166-ec5fb0ab7f5c\",\"text\":\"Oh, it's listening all the time.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"a897375d-3381-4793-a6e2-b8c3e8e606af\",\"sourceId\":\"f21b81f8-c3ad-4642-a1f0-36fbcf80bb08\",\"interview\":\"spk_9\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":27,\"endIdx\":59}]}}],\"number\":15,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"23f80bde-547b-4106-b246-0e4b1c637c3a\",\"title\":\"AI algorithms may limit personal freedom by categorizing individuals.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"3cf95c0c-8df0-43e6-a1e5-474361e6c2cb\",\"text\":\"what if the algorithms become so overbearing [...] they all put you in one little pigeon hole.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"3f16ee0c-5006-4438-9d34-219270251d42\",\"sourceId\":\"e5e60a7b-5580-4b25-b6c1-30515851169a\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":-1,\"endIdx\":93}]}}],\"number\":16,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"5d680102-be47-4f64-82fa-010048dee891\",\"title\":\"Humans have the ability to control AI usage and applications responsibly.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"d42f8ccf-916b-4dfe-86e7-53cb869e498d\",\"text\":\"We can choose whether we use it or not. We can use what can control what we use it for. We can control that, you know, if we use it to, to give us a draft of something that we read it and write it and edit it and use those, those skills[...]\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"b938c154-713e-4c7a-8e24-2ace1bccec11\",\"sourceId\":\"89a27c02-2d5d-43f9-818c-51c605d2b30b\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":-1,\"endIdx\":240}]}}],\"number\":17,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"92576697-926e-4cdf-bdc6-a238d4c6d4ce\",\"title\":\"AI-generated information should meet high accuracy standards to ensure reliability.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"0c8818ce-65c9-45ae-acc3-db17471a006f\",\"text\":\"Coming from a chatbot and bad information coming from a human is still bad information.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"1bd9caa2-5bf4-40f6-a992-8eeacc2f5cdc\",\"sourceId\":\"95a817f8-c7da-42b7-af1d-1d94a9a8b95c\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":0,\"endIdx\":87}]}}],\"number\":18,\"similarClaims\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"eff99729-c620-4e63-98f2-b6cf1017dead\",\"title\":\"Positive Applications\",\"description\":\"Positive Applications\",\"claims\":[{\"id\":\"78dda851-d589-4a83-bd3b-d49d2f43ffde\",\"title\":\"AI has significantly advanced medical research, treatment, and diagnostics.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"0ccbe872-847f-4132-8e06-46ce5ae11dd9\",\"text\":\"Because of how AI has revolutionized medical research and treatment.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"c693acf0-0ad1-4f6c-977f-d769c3c66970\",\"sourceId\":\"2c11de4e-9f28-48cb-8c7c-b4981a1be7ae\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":0,\"endIdx\":68}]}}],\"number\":19,\"similarClaims\":[{\"id\":\"9f5f1285-0a87-4d43-b598-c85c4d2b08be\",\"title\":\"AI has revolutionized medicine.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"d82a6b20-a676-41fd-9ddc-36e50761ac57\",\"text\":\"Medicine has been revolutionized.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"07e69b2b-321b-4646-b00b-165c21201ea7\",\"sourceId\":\"2b4539ad-438e-45ff-b6bf-468e93dfd14e\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":0,\"endIdx\":33}]}}],\"number\":20,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"8fc8b822-8a21-4505-9ee3-5bfcc501fdb0\",\"title\":\"AI can significantly improve healthcare diagnostics.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"8e94939d-f61d-413c-8c79-f2b97484948b\",\"text\":\"AI is here, and you know what, it's going to help diagnose your health issues that much faster and that much better.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"5e54b99a-3725-457a-9cf6-f6fe197d22ae\",\"sourceId\":\"c7f7d56f-e102-47b4-bf41-c0e88141b591\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":175,\"endIdx\":291}]}}],\"number\":21,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"4c5e3d7d-c30d-48f4-83e4-17bded5452fe\",\"title\":\"AI can improve early diagnosis in healthcare, surpassing human abilities.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"e28bf348-7aa0-4b60-9225-96242bb3f6da\",\"text\":\"if you get a cancer diagnosis that was diagnosed early enough that they can treat it because the AI could read it better than a radiologist could, now you're really pro AI\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"586b5d1c-f2ad-48e5-beed-52eb1b26520c\",\"sourceId\":\"caf7fcd8-7510-4d32-ad29-f280268eba85\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":64,\"endIdx\":235}]}}],\"number\":22,\"similarClaims\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"e3df3187-d727-4081-bb3a-b4da33ce2494\",\"title\":\"AI can assist in identifying and intervening in mental health episodes.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"7ee6c0ce-47a6-4d1b-b43d-9bd402c02589\",\"text\":\"People who are bipolar, for example, are going into a manic episode or are going into a depressive episode and potentially could then flag someone to get them help.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"4a90e268-0b63-4795-b157-d4788beede50\",\"sourceId\":\"427aa414-921d-4a73-854e-7ee89839423b\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":0,\"endIdx\":164}]}}],\"number\":23,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"d6f16e44-28a9-4097-9e5f-b98c60d78bda\",\"title\":\"AI education should be a mandatory part of school curriculums.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"7dbdb18b-cb17-4920-baff-2d2b635b6678\",\"text\":\"learning how to use AI responsibly should be part of every Oregon student's education.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"13563c89-a50a-443e-b5d3-f86626721d7e\",\"sourceId\":\"5ef1db23-eb54-4609-a629-3eb20f89c744\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":342,\"endIdx\":428}]}}],\"number\":24,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"bb31b77f-f337-4462-bc18-955fad2dc098\",\"title\":\"AI can be utilized to enhance job prospects through resume rewriting.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"5375e675-8964-4c12-bc4c-953ef56c4f8a\",\"text\":\"you need to have AI help you rewrite your resume\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"35616b19-a059-4233-9ee9-2135b5758f17\",\"sourceId\":\"97e92bac-2985-4077-b81e-d135029cd134\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":3,\"endIdx\":51}]}}],\"number\":25,\"similarClaims\":[]}]}],\"topicColor\":\"brown\"},{\"id\":\"96dea8c4-0e90-4c5e-8cb2-b7800d08a035\",\"title\":\"AI Regulation and Governance\",\"description\":\"AI Regulation and Governance\",\"summary\":\"The discussion on AI Regulation and Governance emphasizes the urgent need for stronger transparency and updated policies, especially in education, to match AI's growing influence. Concerns about AI’s environmental impact due to its high resource consumption are also prevalent. Interestingly, AI companies are actively seeking regulation, highlighting the industry's own recognition of this need. Local policy development is favored, with regional approaches seen as more effective than broad statewide initiatives, offering models for broader policy development. This emphasizes a bottom-up strategy, promoting local governance to address specific issues effectively. The discussion reflects a need for both high-level policy reform and grassroots action to shape AI's future responsibly.\",\"subtopics\":[{\"id\":\"8d59d716-fbc5-487c-86d4-c0f9b96fc2cb\",\"title\":\"Need for Regulation\",\"description\":\"Need for Regulation\",\"claims\":[{\"id\":\"3e767925-2e48-4fd0-bf32-ccb98e9576fc\",\"title\":\"There is a need for stronger transparency and updated policies in AI usage, particularly in education.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"98f679c6-69bb-4261-a3e7-6a33b0b29f3d\",\"text\":\"And there's general agreement on needing stronger transparency on how AI is being used in education.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"43867161-b071-4564-99ff-c85172826934\",\"sourceId\":\"7dea45b1-3734-4214-91cb-20241490969a\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":0,\"endIdx\":100}]}}],\"number\":26,\"similarClaims\":[{\"id\":\"a6d10130-b4f8-457e-9845-c5dbbb97b744\",\"title\":\"Current policies have not kept pace with the influence of AI.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"3ab25c8b-a039-4ab7-8286-65a384b8a5a3\",\"text\":\"policy has not kept up with influence.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"8fb384ca-9fc7-4d46-9483-364c97eb408e\",\"sourceId\":\"96a671f3-c8b8-41dc-8bd1-6a9a69299c11\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":4,\"endIdx\":42}]}}],\"number\":27,\"similarClaims\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"2fadb5fb-2e51-4d26-8247-202855a31f22\",\"title\":\"AI development has significant environmental impacts due to high resource consumption.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"2360f6a5-cd35-4b93-9bba-40a61b7b9d88\",\"text\":\"AI uses so much water, it uses so much electricity, it's bad for the environment.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"391512ac-dc80-43a0-bd5d-32c2fc782090\",\"sourceId\":\"70481745-f212-42b1-9755-6fb96dd4a398\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":102,\"endIdx\":183}]}}],\"number\":28,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"deb8bc99-f29c-4cc5-977c-fa200500fdc9\",\"title\":\"AI companies are seeking proactive regulation from policymakers.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"d4f365d8-113d-4b2c-a508-8b5693c2daba\",\"text\":\"Executives at the AI companies talk to Congress and say, please regulate us.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"77f53cda-3b16-41e7-87bd-ea6070bf1f1f\",\"sourceId\":\"d8768c1e-352f-4fc5-ad02-136956c02455\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":0,\"endIdx\":76}]}}],\"number\":29,\"similarClaims\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"f3158a6e-0b77-43c3-9ad5-813455dd0ada\",\"title\":\"Local Policy Examples\",\"description\":\"Local Policy Examples\",\"claims\":[{\"id\":\"30fa5eab-a6c6-4695-9488-fb3d96f74d04\",\"title\":\"Local governance and regional approaches should be prioritized over broad statewide initiatives for AI policy development.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"1e315496-0601-4700-af36-c187988d3278\",\"text\":\"I'd like to see us focus on Oregon and maybe Central Oregon more than the big mackerel because otherwise you're trying to melt an iceberg with a cigarette lighter.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"22a29006-d765-4eb4-b717-1ca6461178b5\",\"sourceId\":\"5016c0a9-195b-44cc-8f6b-ee2ce836d8a8\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":0,\"endIdx\":163}]}}],\"number\":30,\"similarClaims\":[{\"id\":\"88186ee7-a507-45f0-a57b-bc17ffb85497\",\"title\":\"Regionalizing AI policies is beneficial\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"16972124-123b-40b8-9b61-079d8b79b714\",\"text\":\"to the extent it can be modified or regionalized, maybe that's a good thing.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"fc4659c8-54ba-454a-92e9-9fae4ccd1512\",\"sourceId\":\"81b6280f-a48e-4457-ba2c-696233f335b9\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":102,\"endIdx\":178}]}}],\"number\":31,\"similarClaims\":[]},{\"id\":\"8f94de07-5f96-4c9d-bae0-0f3b2f361dcc\",\"title\":\"Local governance initiatives can serve as models for broader AI policy development.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"30be46a6-e014-4e38-84b5-12a77027d3b8\",\"text\":\"Well, some of the, the local issues that have come up, um, in Bend, for example, where they put in the new, uh, red light cameras.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"3477ca26-55b2-401d-974e-cb4be715f9f3\",\"sourceId\":\"47124cb4-4e75-4383-86bc-b7fef0866b79\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":0,\"endIdx\":130}]}}],\"number\":32,\"similarClaims\":[]}]}]}],\"topicColor\":\"blueSky\"},{\"id\":\"aa116d83-14c2-4770-bc93-6a67c250a841\",\"title\":\"Community Engagement with AI\",\"description\":\"Community Engagement with AI\",\"summary\":\"The discussion on 'Community Engagement with AI' focuses on enhancing access and inclusivity in AI development. A key theme is the need for broadening technology education and incorporating diverse perspectives, with concerns that current AI development often lacks input from marginalized communities. This sentiment underscores the importance of integrating diverse voices to create inclusive AI solutions. Although the conversation touches on community-specific challenges, this area lacks detailed claims and input. Overall, the discourse highlights the necessity of evolving AI collaboratively to ensure it serves the broader community rather than a select few, emphasizing education and representation as pivotal components for equitable engagement.\",\"subtopics\":[{\"id\":\"b6e38480-7840-4e5c-81e3-195256786284\",\"title\":\"Access and Inclusivity\",\"description\":\"Access and Inclusivity\",\"claims\":[{\"id\":\"94ee2bb6-9037-4edb-9e8a-2991822e5e99\",\"title\":\"Broadening technology education and ensuring diverse perspectives in AI development are essential for inclusivity.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"67554d7d-9dd8-4f1a-b27b-7628d32acaa0\",\"text\":\"there's a robotics class and there's a coding class, and you know there are technology classes that are available, but it's not like [...] where just everybody learns it\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"6a726112-0462-4558-a0c3-fefdd8c96015\",\"sourceId\":\"aa5cd789-6218-41a6-a34d-6ec1dad540d3\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":-1,\"endIdx\":168}]}}],\"number\":33,\"similarClaims\":[{\"id\":\"a6eb7107-c474-4006-aac6-a1d189c00b67\",\"title\":\"AI development lacks diverse input from marginalized communities.\",\"quotes\":[{\"id\":\"b9dfd293-5af3-4f8f-b75e-e75c64e85610\",\"text\":\"AI in the information retrieval stage, a lot of it has been put in by white males, not all of it, but a lot of it, but there are a lot of other voices in our community.\",\"reference\":{\"id\":\"e83994ad-96b4-4ce1-a209-e9ae7c61160a\",\"sourceId\":\"ca53b826-9120-4284-811e-5c217568dc68\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"startIdx\":104,\"endIdx\":272}]}}],\"number\":34,\"similarClaims\":[]}]}]}],\"topicColor\":\"greenLeaf\"}],\"sources\":[{\"id\":\"4bce5261-34fb-42d8-9242-5dbf086e4fd8\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah, and I'm not trying to, I'm not trying to challenge you, I'm just trying to, we also have a daughter who's extremely feminist.\"}]},{\"id\":\"7b5d1db8-7398-44cb-b285-bbb3e77911f5\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I mean her concern is that what AI can do is really amplify the voices of just a few people when we're in this community thing we're trying to reach out to the margins and how do we get their voices to get input into AI policy. I'm with you. I, I'm, I, the cancer prediction rates and everything in AI hallelujah. I mean, I love that stuff.\"}]},{\"id\":\"ff699ed7-33cc-4e46-89d0-adeb0ed2f825\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"But I think there are, I think that's what Patty's trying to get to, if I understand is, you know, there are a lot of things that can do well. How do we double down on those and what do we want to be concerned about so that we can get to commissioners and our lawmakers and say, here's what our voice, here's what we're concerned about. Is\"}]},{\"id\":\"11029f5e-94d4-4a9d-990e-4bd7ad4fca2e\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"that exactly. And, and to understand because we all here can do about it,\"}]},{\"id\":\"3a1230be-2400-42de-b668-0c5c51dbf0a4\",\"interview\":\"spk_2\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"huh, there's nothing we can do about it.\"}]},{\"id\":\"12c1cc26-8e11-4293-aca8-b4322ce369c2\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, no one wants to stop it or get rid of it. What this is is a format of people to talk about their, to learn about it and to talk about how it can be used.\"}]},{\"id\":\"96b26d88-b08f-4a1d-92b0-5c63ba196deb\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"In this, in our community in a good way. No one's trying to get rid of it.\"}]},{\"id\":\"cd90d7d8-cad7-48e1-a10c-f873d27a6814\",\"interview\":\"spk_2\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well,\"}]},{\"id\":\"956fd3af-f57a-48a0-b190-b22b20e41894\",\"interview\":\"spk_2\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I appreciate that.\"}]},{\"id\":\"cf174dbb-fec6-4234-9605-efacc8bfe8e8\",\"interview\":\"spk_2\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So are we going to make a list of the things that are, are we're scared about and then\"}]},{\"id\":\"deca0dd6-548d-4200-835d-f99f6d1a457c\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"uh all the things we think it'll be good for and all the things we think are concerning. I\"}]},{\"id\":\"01457fe2-b943-4d4a-9628-1ffc34e151ed\",\"interview\":\"spk_2\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"think the good is going to far outweigh the bad. Oh,\"}]},{\"id\":\"09077ef6-bb8a-431e-b9b6-31df4646239f\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I hope so too.\"}]},{\"id\":\"1918bdfd-459a-4350-9542-28876284cd5a\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I think we all hope that and\"}]},{\"id\":\"d333271f-78be-4989-adf0-0b611cabe362\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"and that's, you know, one of the reasons why we're talking to a lot of people is there are some people who are all for it and there are some people who are absolutely against it for a bunch of different reasons and ultimately we're all going to have to live with it. So you know how can we surface those issues and correct the misconceptions and you know make it palatable for.\"}]},{\"id\":\"91877938-12a1-49fa-be4a-d5f87cf57561\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Everybody and put whatever policies need to be in place to make that happen, you know, there's a proposal right now in Congress to have a moratorium on data centers, for example, that, you know, they're, they're the idea is to slow down AI development. I'm not sure it would actually accomplish that, but you know there are people trying to control it. There are schools that are embracing it. There are schools that are outlawing it.\"}]},{\"id\":\"eb63db4d-66ab-402d-95c6-34856fd7d99f\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"There are, um, organizations that embrace it for hiring, for reviewing, um, resumes and, and things like that, and there are organizations who don't, you know, who believe that that should be done by a human.\"}]},{\"id\":\"ec51c2bf-9bb2-4280-ba6f-a99478c02732\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Um, so lots of perspectives and that's what we're here to capture.\"}]},{\"id\":\"5016c0a9-195b-44cc-8f6b-ee2ce836d8a8\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I'd like to see us focus on Oregon and maybe Central Oregon more than the big mackerel because otherwise you're trying to melt an iceberg with a cigarette lighter.\"}]},{\"id\":\"81b6280f-a48e-4457-ba2c-696233f335b9\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"hard to do, but maybe there's something we can do that controls the people who control this, and, and to the extent it can be modified or regionalized, maybe that's a good thing.\"}]},{\"id\":\"47124cb4-4e75-4383-86bc-b7fef0866b79\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, some of the, the local issues that have come up, um, in Bend, for example, where they put in the new, uh, red light cameras.\"}]},{\"id\":\"41be01e3-e6ee-43a7-97fb-dff5912d12e5\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And there was, I guess, a determination made that they would not use AI to analyze that footage, but then they forgot to flip that switch and they ended up, somebody used it to um find someone that was undocumented by following their car. So, you know, that's an example of a, a local policy where you could say, you know, yes, we totally want to be able to track.\"}]},{\"id\":\"40200ca4-dcb9-4121-bf21-1a526af1db0c\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"People because crime's a problem, or we'd say, you know, that's taking it too far.\"}]},{\"id\":\"37de1579-61f8-4599-b046-70abe0e31e90\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And it's not, should AI exist or not, it's should we be using it for this application or\"}]},{\"id\":\"1b79f3f5-6d81-4911-b6e8-13ad1c791ac0\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, AI is kind of like a hammer. You can use it to drive nails. You could also use it to bash people in the head. And so I mean, we're not talking about the tool, we're talking about the way it's used, the\"}]},{\"id\":\"ecc9357c-bcd0-4068-847c-c638f7cb1170\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"implementation, exactly, exactly. That's a good point.\"}]},{\"id\":\"5ef1db23-eb54-4609-a629-3eb20f89c744\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"All right. So to give you some, just a little perspective on the open poll, um, I talked about what it is already. Um, as I mentioned, we have a little over 300 responses and what we've seen, and I'm not not gonna give you a bunch of data on this, but just what we've seen is there are some questions where there's general disagreement, like learning how to use AI responsibly should be part of every Oregon student's education.\"}]},{\"id\":\"379a3e09-cda6-4e40-a7d6-0bf2c4177800\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"OK. The results from the poll are showing currently, some people agree and some people really don't agree with that.\"}]},{\"id\":\"cda6d59f-714d-4c78-8ef7-f6fb019a4e74\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Um, the same, you know, I don't think AI has benefits that outweigh the environmental and social reproduction or repercussions. Um, so,\"}]},{\"id\":\"d755ae82-3b3a-4c67-9b6d-5d3dc02ebd73\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yes, some people think the good things are are more good than the bad things are bad, and some people think it's, it's the other way around. Um.\"}]},{\"id\":\"4580dc23-9080-49be-a36b-15ac6cd3f078\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"There are also areas of general agreement, like workers should have the right to know when AI is being used to evaluate their performance or productivity.\"}]},{\"id\":\"6da2b4f3-4c4e-43a4-82a0-b6f0a4491d30\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"OK, general agreement on that. Um,\"}]},{\"id\":\"e911b72c-b0ab-4238-a7b4-dea4a22f59cc\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Related to data centers, which is, you know, not really an AI topic, but is, is kind of in the, the Venn diagram of, of AI. Um, data centers are currently required to report their water usage. They should also be required to report their electrical usage. OK? There's general agreement on that. Um.\"}]},{\"id\":\"7dea45b1-3734-4214-91cb-20241490969a\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And there's general agreement on needing stronger transparency on how AI is being used in education. OK? So that's just kind of an example of where, what we're seeing in the poll already.\"}]},{\"id\":\"40a3abb8-d4e3-483f-bb31-125f0768ac4c\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"OK, so, show of hands, how often do you use AI? Any nevers?\"}]},{\"id\":\"7b4b4cbb-8d6b-4599-a60a-1af59e9b947d\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, it depends on what you call AI.\"}]},{\"id\":\"5e719d8d-5831-4dc2-948f-a15a5f21637a\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, that's true. If you use Google Maps, you use AI or, you know, any kind of mapping program. If you use most search engines, you're using it. Um, if you use the, um,\"}]},{\"id\":\"47dcad9a-d591-4fdd-965c-aaadd0c70372\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"chatbots on most websites you're using it. Um, if you're, I think, uh, kind of what we're using is the, the benchmark here is, you know, do you go into cloud or chat GPT or co-pilot or whatever and talk to it, ask it questions, get help. I'm sorry, YouTube is, is another one of those that's using AI.\"}]},{\"id\":\"2f6a39f0-79ca-4572-9eac-b614c96ef2dd\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Not necessarily overtly, right?\"}]},{\"id\":\"f2f10fc5-c4bb-4bc4-84f4-ab262bcdb314\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I don't think you know necessarily because so much of it, I don't know what percentage it is, but there's so much there that's controlling stuff. If you go on Facebook or YouTube or any of that stuff, um, there's something that has come through some kind of AI, including fabricated pictures.\"}]},{\"id\":\"08d81ee2-fc32-4eda-9d35-d9016a9431cf\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"They're very, very good. You can't even tell if they're real anymore, you know, there's no copyright. There's no credits, there's no nothing, you know, and I picture, uh, you know, some 19 year old guy living in his mother's basement or something, you know, doing all this stuff, and, you know, I really don't know what it is, but to me it's just scary as hell what could happen.\"}]},{\"id\":\"d443ef81-3383-441f-99ee-a4bf9ea96e79\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"You basically don't know.\"}]},{\"id\":\"533e02f2-d906-4f14-a52f-2af3a4d1d7c0\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Especially since some of those 19 year old guys wind up being billionaires, and they spent so much time in their basement that they don't know, you know, anything about dealing with people and, you\"}]},{\"id\":\"ada5398a-9c23-410e-b0f4-6cc7361b51d2\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"know, yep, yep, and good for them. I don't begrudge Bill Gates anything at all. He changed the world,\"}]},{\"id\":\"8c63de5f-878d-463d-868a-5dd8a2bbcce4\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"but he's a good guy, really.\"}]},{\"id\":\"43a7d547-e3d7-4bda-aeeb-4ab4a4f88731\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"He's OK,\"}]},{\"id\":\"cc2b6182-0164-46f3-84e9-ecddd676df3b\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"yeah, except for that whole Jeffrey Epstein thing.\"}]},{\"id\":\"b502aef1-5781-44df-a534-5309f2e8ba0c\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"That's another, you know, Bill Gates and Jeffrey Epstein, um, so who here uses a, a chatbot?\"}]},{\"id\":\"f34edba1-8844-45f7-8712-82aed1a44c7d\",\"interview\":\"spk_2\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"People are innocent until they're proven guilty.\"}]},{\"id\":\"e8f6a3c1-d57c-4d99-af82-84c0b8e5af27\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Oh, that's yeah. Well, that is, yes, so um I use Google Maps with some frequency. I love maps just in books, in anything. I could stare at maps, so I do use Google Maps. I don't do any chatbot or.\"}]},{\"id\":\"0f7f243a-1bc1-4bc2-bd88-a81645f1eae8\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I don't, and I look at YouTube once in a while.\"}]},{\"id\":\"c6f3a432-d195-479b-8232-952b10bf12a5\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Do you ever miss a paper map?\"}]},{\"id\":\"3abd7a8f-65fb-4d63-ae98-e33ef92bc6ce\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"No, because I have paper maps. I just, yeah, yeah,\"}]},{\"id\":\"d62a262b-b0ea-4b90-a308-b89bd89bb80c\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I do miss it sometimes.\"}]},{\"id\":\"539d50b3-dc92-43a2-9a7c-f5226ed9b570\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"We could have a whole map discussion. I have a, like a, a high level philosophical thought you\"}]},{\"id\":\"30c0d647-1127-4cdc-a027-ada51546def9\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"have Google, but then you think about the times when you just used to have the paper map and it seemed, I don't know. Right. Right. I still use it. But I, I just, sometimes I miss them. Yeah,\"}]},{\"id\":\"41f6edc5-a415-4ca2-9107-54a1dc02c8c7\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I still use them. Yeah. We keep an atlas handy. Yeah.\"}]},{\"id\":\"fa5fa7b6-e79f-4932-960c-2e91e6660063\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Like you have an atlas on the backseat of the truck\"}]},{\"id\":\"fa94c67f-fc7c-4a17-aca1-64e87a888f8b\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"the laps. Thomas guide. We're\"}]},{\"id\":\"36883eec-4fad-47cd-9dbf-5ff0dbfb6ead\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"all at the age,\"}]},{\"id\":\"392dc7c4-8975-4ec5-b688-b97311b3cf7c\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I think that we have an\"}]},{\"id\":\"1c927a9e-d7bc-4487-b051-a30219e66fe8\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"appreciation for\"}]},{\"id\":\"73bd2e33-b09d-4e62-bb27-576d64ba2551\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"paper maps. So, Suzie,\"}]},{\"id\":\"de3567f1-4a97-4cbe-a6a5-23917eab7bc3\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"We were talking about\"}]},{\"id\":\"966b633d-d6ba-4221-9348-e40644cb0acc\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"using. So,\"}]},{\"id\":\"dcc2093c-6c88-4aae-a9af-cc5152fa6859\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"so let's say I have someone who has a subject matter that I'm, I'm trying to get my point across. I'm trying to be, you know, try to figure it out. A lot of times by putting it in chat GPT. I don't do it all the time. I'm saying probably, well, if you're talking about maps and all of that, probably, who knows?\"}]},{\"id\":\"922009d8-cebc-4e07-8b34-c9187a46e9d3\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Maybe. Well, I mean, but let's say.\"}]},{\"id\":\"826a53d0-8ec2-4a1c-b534-601760a0e9fc\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Direct intentional. It's\"}]},{\"id\":\"2be9207f-4756-4b7b-af7c-67834e64463c\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"interaction. It's\"}]},{\"id\":\"3e2457c6-f672-4eaa-bbbe-389dca5fe0aa\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"really nice because it's like that other opinion. Um-hum. And so I'll read that and I'll incorporate part of it. I still don't incorporate all of it, but it's a nice other opinion to have. And it might be that they make a point that you're trying to make, but they make it better. Um-hum. Um-hum. So, yes. Yes. Yeah. I, I use that and it helps particularly,\"}]},{\"id\":\"31fa9486-2ff8-4824-897b-59670a6a38a9\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"In a difficult where someone's very passionate about something, it maybe helps you get more of a, uh, I don't know, like I say, it's another opinion of trying to get it back to that person. Sure.\"}]},{\"id\":\"7b1e7abd-7d3d-4cd0-9f9e-c1e090c2dece\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And Mike, you talked about using it for your job description.\"}]},{\"id\":\"39e22e0c-e156-449b-a177-76ee03304680\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah, um, the Presbyterian Church on the Warm Springs is undergoing renewal and we're at a point looking for a pastor.\"}]},{\"id\":\"1bd4463c-8ab5-4118-b4e3-b7bce36764f2\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"There's a lot about that culture that I know I don't know a lot and wanted to get and so I just asked AI put in Warm Springs reservation looking for a pastor. Here's the experience and within 10 seconds.\"}]},{\"id\":\"98f37fcb-4f68-4d31-bd4c-7fe7c0a115a0\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"There's a, there's a posting.\"}]},{\"id\":\"482415e1-73ba-4a8c-a7c2-9d7c9d1d478d\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"When you say I just asked AI, were you using a search engine? Did you like Google it or something?\"}]},{\"id\":\"79a42c5d-2c59-4b9e-9bf2-b8e084ff1820\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah, I just went to Google and\"}]},{\"id\":\"45c56d48-0843-4b45-b6c5-092cbfdabd2e\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"AI. OK, so that counts as AI,\"}]},{\"id\":\"9c64b962-9a88-465d-946c-fe48cd00cc7a\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"uh, that one was directly using that.\"}]},{\"id\":\"cc596031-dc23-4dfb-bc3b-a4b2c1c18a71\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So that's using Gemini, which is part of Google,\"}]},{\"id\":\"a5ccd4b5-6c78-4998-be8c-050ce3680187\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"and I took probably 75 or 80% of that, tuned up a few things, but I, I felt it was like a bunch of hyper caffeinated steroid-driven research reference librarians.\"}]},{\"id\":\"f12686d4-7ef6-425a-8eab-759662c0af2b\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"That were turned loose and came right\"}]},{\"id\":\"659e7d2f-8020-42ea-b3f0-3a94484d701d\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"back.\"}]},{\"id\":\"cea39c9a-3ec4-40f5-a1d9-0a03ef5b8e76\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"But you're right, there's a totally different culture there, and it's very, you need to understand it and, and, and you have a limited understanding because we haven't lived that. I've, I've learned that in COYC because we have the tribes represented and it's, I'm always asking questions.\"}]},{\"id\":\"a6dcccc9-c467-4010-828f-6690203bec6b\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah, that was\"}]},{\"id\":\"a8be83da-5533-4c0d-ae5e-216ddab8db2d\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"it. It helps bridge that gap. Yeah,\"}]},{\"id\":\"9a9ddd07-c754-4639-815e-014875e25f45\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"yeah, it helps me find a lot of answers to questions. Whether they're correct answers, I don't know, but it gets me pointed in that direction.\"}]},{\"id\":\"2bcfdcf7-a6d3-4c5a-a503-e672bad729a7\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, then you can take it to your contact in the tribes and, and ask them to, to vet it. And it's kind of like translation, you know, you can Google translate things, but you will be embarrassed if you then put it out there without having someone who's at least.\"}]},{\"id\":\"dacfacd5-f2a1-4a2c-badb-6dcffbd3a85d\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Reasonably fluent in the language, actually reading it, a human.\"}]},{\"id\":\"488bb2a6-a432-4d69-b87a-7e91b3678ac9\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"You put it out and then somebody, somebody comes back. Why do you want to kick my horse?\"}]},{\"id\":\"8c900f83-e430-4f20-8b06-9a5105e68701\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Exactly, exactly, Kat, how about you?\"}]},{\"id\":\"a9b65c7e-b6f1-4965-affd-89baf2ed28de\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Um, I use it sometimes just to, you know, like.\"}]},{\"id\":\"7d072d0c-d66f-4d5d-9e1e-aefebf68efb6\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"What does blah blah blah mean and then you ask, you know, your little, your little micro para para and it gives you we look that's usually um\"}]},{\"id\":\"83797d8d-5b40-499a-9a02-d12c95b6a6a8\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Anyway, uh, Wikipedia. Wikipedia, thank you. And so you know that there's a source that they, that that's coming from too. So, but sometimes you don't get the right, the right\"}]},{\"id\":\"bd2e89cf-a6d8-4018-b1ba-7273498b277a\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"answers. That's true. So that's true. Just like when you're getting help from a human. Exactly.\"}]},{\"id\":\"7baa3b24-6293-4b38-a676-73bc7a650160\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, so far AI basically is based on humans, that, that in other words, the stuff on how to write is based on, you know, what millions of people have written, yep.\"}]},{\"id\":\"64c092b5-4605-4ea7-aa70-6d89292ecbdb\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And so uh you know, from that standpoint, it's still humans are indirectly involved.\"}]},{\"id\":\"9fa18e8a-0afc-4336-9d08-93dd956e9a86\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Absolutely, Doug, for you and Patty. I get\"}]},{\"id\":\"e340b4e0-7988-4814-851b-decc259c55ec\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"very frustrated when I'm writing something and, and I'm a pretty good writer and uh it'll it'll come up and say, well, how about this, or give me a bunch of words that, you know, I didn't want. It slows me down and I've tried to delete some things and there's one that goes and I've forgotten.\"}]},{\"id\":\"49270335-d00e-40bb-a030-457afa037252\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Name of the program, but I can't get rid of the darn thing and I tried and tried and you know it's just to me it's frustrating, uh, but then there's other stuff when you're just sitting there and you want to know something like, like, um, um, I like to watch airplanes fly around and read about them and stuff and so I went on the other day and I, I said, uh, what, what's the list of the best short takeoff and landing, uh, passenger airplanes in the world.\"}]},{\"id\":\"b268a419-6b4f-4648-a162-cfe8eb64c727\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, I get a whole bunch of stuff back and, you know, it wasn't exactly what I was looking for, but, you know, I watch them land at other places. I mean, it's just I'm passing the time while I'm watching a ball game or something, but, uh, I get frustrated when somebody's doing my thinking. Um-hum. And, and that, that just irritates me to the point sometimes I want to just, you know, throw the thing on the floor or quit, you know, I, I don't know, it's, I mean,\"}]},{\"id\":\"30cbf41f-a91f-49b6-8fa9-860f8d489ba6\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Here to stay and I accept that and there's probably gonna be a lot more good, for example, medical. I think, uh, now I just had an annual medical thing over in Redmond the other day and, uh, I got back stuff and, and, uh, the radiologist read everything and it's all good and all that, but I'll bet you $100 to 20 cents there was uh some kind of an AI coming back from that after I was looking at the ultrasound and all that stuff. Yeah so.\"}]},{\"id\":\"a5a6224d-2139-40af-b2a4-d414a75f8d32\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"You know, and I, and I can't distinguish between a human being and a machine. And I also, I, you know, when, when you get old, as a lot of us are in this room, you know, there's certain things that are never gonna get replaced by, by this thing, and, you know, I, I don't see a, uh, uh, artificial intelligence up at the pulpit preaching.\"}]},{\"id\":\"34c4409b-156a-40b4-8525-a4c082164db6\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I may be wrong, but\"}]},{\"id\":\"3a40e7a3-8344-4350-bedb-4817799dd1ef\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I don't know. There are,\"}]},{\"id\":\"26c206df-9a1f-4dac-9ffb-59826dd4936c\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"no, I appreciate that because I also did some work as a chaplain, and there are chaplain models, and in Japan there are a lot of people who are turning to AI companions as,\"}]},{\"id\":\"56f3bd88-c202-40b1-a2d7-57830cde57af\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"what about the human aspect? You, well, no,\"}]},{\"id\":\"1091290e-c4f3-42ff-9192-b453f346d1aa\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"for me that's exactly\"}]},{\"id\":\"c91b60b4-f942-47e7-8793-9a9a552b264c\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"it. That's,\"}]},{\"id\":\"9853152c-5d51-48c9-b7c5-a8b564172db0\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"so you, I'm sure you've done funerals, and there's a point where you go up to the person who lost someone, a loved one, and you touch them.\"}]},{\"id\":\"540a907f-d748-4db7-a3ff-db73783ddaa0\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Mhm. Now how do you, uh, that's never gonna get replaced, is it?\"}]},{\"id\":\"119adac9-a1a1-42c0-886f-d3e499b93d42\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"For no, that's for me is the big question in my own little world, and I don't want to get it because I know we have a bigger, but where's the organic human spirit component in this, especially if it's retrieving a bunch of information and then thinking for itself based on just all this statistical information. Where does the organic come into?\"}]},{\"id\":\"64596fa5-58d1-4174-8e95-62923922f40e\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Or\"}]},{\"id\":\"f9a1cad7-8a82-4132-b8a8-bb6544b9b347\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"spiritual or whatever\"}]},{\"id\":\"d6870092-cc72-4f83-9ac3-d38344de8728\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"you want to call it just plain compassion and empathy for other human beings.\"}]},{\"id\":\"ca243b1a-dcc2-4daf-b207-ec94b8998efa\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, yeah, exactly. I mean AI can't be expected to have compassion.\"}]},{\"id\":\"cb79bf8c-6138-4711-b5f5-8e1d3894fbd6\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"It can give you verbal answers that might provide comfort, but\"}]},{\"id\":\"719f08b2-c11c-4b4c-9f2d-a3e6a0e441f6\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"what, but, but it can't, uh.\"}]},{\"id\":\"301dbead-6a50-480d-933a-1cda7d605ead\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Can't, you know, I mean, it can't feel, yeah,\"}]},{\"id\":\"f3afa047-5516-422e-8935-6e08c9a2b6fb\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"no, no, but people that are using it and not, not socializing at all, that's, um, that's what's real to them, but they don't even, I don't think they realize I'm thinking of younger people mainly.\"}]},{\"id\":\"95633406-a3d3-4c4e-baab-9c3960e2dd7e\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"That they could be any age, um, where that's their only interaction is through their computer or their phone.\"}]},{\"id\":\"d4c8fa62-c426-41f1-9a84-3ee869c12380\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And I think that is an extremely valid point. So it used to be you went to the airport and you sat down and you're waiting for a plane, and I'd go, hey, where are you going? Well, I'm going to Cincinnati to see my mother. Where are you going? Well, I'm going to Hawaii to learn how to hula. People.\"}]},{\"id\":\"23de50b1-3451-4118-80cf-3cae889f9db1\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"People interacted and for short times or sitting in the bus stop or whatever it is and now you look and I really am concerned about this. You look at our young people and they're like this, and Senator Merkley said something to me that I had not thought about, but we were talking about education, and he said what happens with education is you have these children and they have these video games and everything.\"}]},{\"id\":\"aebb58ab-cdd9-44f3-9c3e-5fda88880512\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"It's just really fast paced, going like this, like this, and they get in and they're learning their, let's just say ABCs, and it's like, well this is sort of boring. This is slow\"}]},{\"id\":\"a607a5bf-131b-402f-bdbf-c9ed1afbf7c9\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"paced, boring as\"}]},{\"id\":\"30e384ec-6d70-4f12-865f-b9a7d166a430\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"hell, you know, and I thought it was an excellent point. I mean, I was very, you know, impressed in that, like I say, it was Senator Merkley, and he makes a very valid point, and I think that you lose a lot of that socialization.\"}]},{\"id\":\"f4a31078-1100-4797-8b71-e826145f8666\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And again, just having a part of another human being for maybe 10 minutes having a cup of coffee somewhere or whatever, that is what's really missing and that is a pity on all of society and that's your compassion because how do you have compassion if you haven't talked to someone else and gotten to have that little bit of time with them.\"}]},{\"id\":\"305166fe-34e7-4103-bbeb-5a49a1c73c56\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"As a quick aside, I also sit on the homeless shelter board of directors, and I know that is a very politically divisive, but I had a conversation not long ago with somebody who has a different view, but we had a conversation in person and recognized, you know, our goals are the same. It's just how do you get there? We have some different thoughts about it, but you lose that, I think, if you don't have that empathy, that compassion, if it's just all information retrieval.\"}]},{\"id\":\"5d31c721-9377-4b13-9426-b8222ca75077\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Um, haven't they found that, um,\"}]},{\"id\":\"314fa01f-d326-461b-b6ab-a3f24a734863\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Because this has been going on for a while and kids with their cell phones and using their cell phones in class, and haven't they found in some of those schools where you don't get to have your cell phone in class\"}]},{\"id\":\"48054e6b-f188-44a5-a250-bd4df1a83c8b\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"and you're not becoming trains\"}]},{\"id\":\"0f64f5b6-34d2-4b47-bfb3-70cd93215e7a\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"are\"}]},{\"id\":\"34dd4248-5071-45fb-b813-a1eb63ec51da\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"talking to each other again and looking up instead of at their phone all the time. So, um, and how.\"}]},{\"id\":\"4dbd3fe8-50eb-45f8-b4f9-a346b74943fb\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Important that is because you need to have that if you're gonna be right with the world I guess is what I'm thinking um you need to have that interaction with humans and talking about job job resumes and being reviewed and blah blah blah well how old was I? 50.\"}]},{\"id\":\"dc107056-3029-40f1-8dcc-93b0e46417c2\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"When we went to seminary, yeah, yeah, and I had to leave my job and go into the Bay Area and look for a new job and everything was by computer and I was used to face to face and um when\"}]},{\"id\":\"15995f64-f3b3-45b9-8419-2b25f06acc63\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"we went to Bank of America and we mentioned when we were opening the account and the teller said, oh, we're hiring and she was like looking at Kathleen like you'd be great here.\"}]},{\"id\":\"1207f71b-8365-483a-a7e1-27967c2674c7\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"It didn't quantify that when she went to.\"}]},{\"id\":\"f76bec56-63ef-47ec-9e5a-53a467aba29d\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"No,\"}]},{\"id\":\"79e754d8-e26e-4fe3-b3ac-72442fb5ce8f\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"we didn't even get\"}]},{\"id\":\"84a7c32e-98d3-4427-bc2b-8b7dd6205b7d\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"an interview. Yeah. Yeah. So, that's that same type of.\"}]},{\"id\":\"c7d8ecaf-f13c-4f98-8bbf-da12a7b373c4\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"No, it's. And when I finally did get to have an interview, and it was because I called an agency that it was,\"}]},{\"id\":\"c5e8759b-a8e4-4097-a5c9-735e6568fc93\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"The same kind of agency that I worked for in the other county but it was in a different county but it wasn't the same agency. Um, and it's for child care services and\"}]},{\"id\":\"1b6443f5-bc87-451f-9348-d6355ac9ea82\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I had emailed them before I even moved there, didn't hear anything, and then I did again later and they said, oh, you know what, um, bring us in your resume and um we'll see, and I did and I met somebody and it was that interaction and and the the person that was helping.\"}]},{\"id\":\"8eb37349-9134-47b7-9741-04e4adbf25f8\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"me do all this, um, said, you know, once people meet you, cat, it's good, it's just when you everything that's on paper, it doesn't show so there's something about that face to face human thing that happens\"}]},{\"id\":\"97e92bac-2985-4077-b81e-d135029cd134\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"or you need to have AI help you rewrite your resume\"}]},{\"id\":\"2be20bb0-813b-4f41-aa48-2a24fd95dbdb\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"they didn't have it when I was.\"}]},{\"id\":\"3abc0c49-ba8f-43a5-8ce2-6c7c2637a77e\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"No, I, I'm, I'm with you.\"}]},{\"id\":\"e639f559-6374-4604-8348-7457d751604f\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Patty, do you want to share your experience? Oh, OK. I have my place\"}]},{\"id\":\"bffb772f-daee-4532-abac-fc6f3a1f75ae\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"in society.\"}]},{\"id\":\"858abaf0-6416-479c-9836-bd945275d740\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"That's fine. Gordon. How about you? Are you an AI user?\"}]},{\"id\":\"7b0378ee-0e57-4148-9a8f-a207953ba9d5\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Uh, are you, well, yeah, I use it to a certain extent. One thing though, I refuse to do.\"}]},{\"id\":\"36ded3ef-e9aa-4712-a6a5-8547703fa9ec\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I've made my career largely was based on writing. I was a, a land use planner, you know, and did a lot of writing, did a lot of things. I absolutely refuse to use AI in any way when it comes to writing. Because I think I'm a better writer than AI. Yeah.\"}]},{\"id\":\"f12d5863-e0c0-4488-a31b-a9f1a9bee26e\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"But, but the point is, and also I, I don't want to see it replacing humans writing because writing is a wonderful skill and it's something I really enjoy. Um-hum. Of course, it'll probably have, of course, the same way. I mean, everybody probably worried that photography would replace painting.\"}]},{\"id\":\"c372165f-082e-4d5d-8a0e-9ff7322992c1\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And it didn't really because obviously people like I know a lady who writes stuff, you know, is a member of a writer's group, and I don't think she has any intention of publishing, but I mean you can still write for fun, but still kids don't learn to write. That's the other problem. Kids are people aren't going to learn to write and they're not gonna learn how wonderful it is to be able to use words, you know, to, you know, to express what you mean.\"}]},{\"id\":\"736eacae-df80-4906-a590-dbe70f94b0ae\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"That takes a lot of, it takes a lot of thought, you know, what word and what phrase do I use, you know, here, and, and I think you might lose that with AI. Yeah,\"}]},{\"id\":\"d4bd98c9-5648-4720-a436-3c0e93100fec\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"quite possibly.\"}]},{\"id\":\"800bff9b-c428-44cb-a651-c1b10d064d0e\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Gary, how about you? I,\"}]},{\"id\":\"04c2766d-1f25-4f70-bf0e-a250e159632c\",\"interview\":\"spk_9\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I'm concerned because I don't think that I use AI frequently, but\"}]},{\"id\":\"1671578f-c4e2-4ea8-811a-900a23cf0146\",\"interview\":\"spk_9\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"When I look at the stuff up on the screen, I probably use it all the time, and that bothers me.\"}]},{\"id\":\"2d453549-c960-4bea-b140-85b76f358c41\",\"interview\":\"spk_9\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And I, I don't know why it bothers me.\"}]},{\"id\":\"51802067-adda-4cea-b7e4-ba8984bd1a0e\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I wonder if it's almost like because you don't have a choice. It just is popping up on things and you don't even question it. And it's not like, did you want?\"}]},{\"id\":\"2598f97c-12d3-4ff9-b2d1-8c4204c51d1a\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"An AI answer? What's an AI answer, you know, and so.\"}]},{\"id\":\"1a97981b-4634-466b-9930-9725acde5e3f\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I think that's it's like it's taking something away from you that you didn't have a choice about.\"}]},{\"id\":\"1988a96b-af27-4002-bc40-0df73b4a039f\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Absolutely.\"}]},{\"id\":\"5a102b82-bbc8-4981-bf3f-56862a1e3382\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So, I\"}]},{\"id\":\"3be82ce1-1a3d-45eb-97f7-beb1bccf9e15\",\"interview\":\"spk_9\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"OK.\"}]},{\"id\":\"b3270f2c-7737-45f6-8d59-1360382005fe\",\"interview\":\"spk_9\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I'm perplexed.\"}]},{\"id\":\"13e8e463-7749-4a15-82b0-1fac60e7d9c1\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"OK. That's a fine place to be. I think to some degree we're all perplexed on this, right? Mark, how about\"}]},{\"id\":\"6e2a8ad7-1853-4816-952f-df1a98fe4c97\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"you?\"}]},{\"id\":\"457a5014-8962-4879-93cf-61ff28f281a0\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Uh, well, I've really learned to appreciate AI more recently, um, a couple of practical situations, uh, how AI has contributed to, uh, the application of the global positioning system.\"}]},{\"id\":\"75c555ec-53bc-478f-a8ee-853ef7c6ffa0\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And pieces of equipment that rely on that.\"}]},{\"id\":\"5a2e5ce2-174c-4b0d-be8b-0117035a4d75\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"It's, it's a bummer to be lost in the wilderness and it's great to be found, and I've experienced that on more than one occasion.\"}]},{\"id\":\"c78a204b-e9ca-446f-b28d-210b9475e9f1\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"It's life saving. Um, I had a different life saving experience over here at Saint Charles Hospital last month when I went in with a bellyache and that wouldn't go away and I had been eating less and less over about a week's time but feeling more and more full.\"}]},{\"id\":\"57c6f8af-42fb-4a41-a58d-4c675dd076df\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And, um,\"}]},{\"id\":\"816aa115-e7ed-43ba-b25c-54df6124be46\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"The short story is, um.\"}]},{\"id\":\"2c11de4e-9f28-48cb-8c7c-b4981a1be7ae\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Because of how AI has revolutionized medical research and treatment.\"}]},{\"id\":\"0ed7c6d8-52f6-4b6a-afb2-5deceabff6f4\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Um, the staff there were able to locate, uh, two life-threatening blood clots.\"}]},{\"id\":\"eb1e9f07-8328-4524-ae27-27b12633b8d0\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And yet not be able to diagnose what caused them.\"}]},{\"id\":\"fff42466-9977-4770-b3b8-dbe98c930d34\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So I was treated.\"}]},{\"id\":\"fa33f6b6-5e30-4bf2-9550-a1522510c559\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And there was no question in any of the doctors' minds, if you had delayed 24 hours.\"}]},{\"id\":\"5217b3a0-c0e4-42a1-9941-f7165da9e279\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"You would have likely end up in an emergency surgery and your chances would not have even been fifty-fifty to survive that.\"}]},{\"id\":\"1645364d-49c3-4b89-a4ed-c4746375f7d5\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So that was a fascinating introduction to how.\"}]},{\"id\":\"2b4539ad-438e-45ff-b6bf-468e93dfd14e\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Medicine has been revolutionized.\"}]},{\"id\":\"cfc1f611-cb7e-4b6a-b68b-e8abc4bfc447\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"But it's a tool in the doctor's hands. You still need the doctor.\"}]},{\"id\":\"297cdfe8-a38f-4aa4-8376-d8142b3ea814\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah, and they've shared a lot more information than I've ever had in the past, so that now, you know, I have access, um.\"}]},{\"id\":\"1dd02454-cd0e-4a6d-9df7-53d429c3e2b6\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Even from that first day in the emergency room to the Mayo Clinic in Rochester, Minnesota with a research unit that's focused on these exact formation of abdominal blood clots and how to get them resolved.\"}]},{\"id\":\"1c1aab8c-98eb-4f29-bc66-b13105ea3549\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Uh, as well as, uh, OHSU was involved with that, so my chart here at Saint Charles, I'm, I'm getting messages posted from labs at OHSU as well as Mayo Clinic, uh.\"}]},{\"id\":\"1f56a1d6-370d-416d-be81-15ebf68d7f72\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"That type of access was not available even just months ago.\"}]},{\"id\":\"0518a49c-d91a-4bb3-96fc-d3458b47eecb\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Sure.\"}]},{\"id\":\"89613ae2-7fcb-46ba-aa86-0518940feaf5\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Absolutely. Well, good. So everybody's got some experience with it.\"}]},{\"id\":\"986f2d9e-ce18-4fa6-bcd7-112c3f3f5ff1\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Let's talk about some of the, the trade-offs. You know, as I mentioned earlier, there are lots of different ways that AI impacts our lives. Um, here are some, and there are others. Do any of these resonate for you in terms of the, the things that you think of first? Um, you know, for you, Mark, it might be that healthcare and medical care piece, right, because\"}]},{\"id\":\"21fd95d4-11e8-4154-8c7e-99ed3978a715\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Because that's a high priority. But, you know, for the rest of you, when, when AI comes up, where does your head go immediately? Is it, you know, related to the impact on employment or on education or on mental health or, you know, what's the, the priority, kind of the, the thing that's floating at the top for you?\"}]},{\"id\":\"a5c95ca9-cbfc-4ff5-b417-8862ad66ffc8\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, another problem that I've had, well, with with with generally AI depends on on formulas.\"}]},{\"id\":\"60a3e7e3-3b62-4193-81b9-75734248a0f3\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"It's, it's fun because, well, there's an analogy, years ago, they believed that you could some people believed that you could tell anything about a person's personality by their handwriting. Yeah.\"}]},{\"id\":\"2ed68ddc-ce0d-4937-ab65-74452738138b\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And that hurt a lot of people because they wrote books on how to analyze someone's personality by handwriting. I think that it turned out to be pretty much nonsense, but a lot of people couldn't get jobs because their handwriting happened was too slanted or something, you know, well, this guy's a psychopath.\"}]},{\"id\":\"c92595d0-413b-4b3b-8d50-bce7ac80ddcf\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Because I could have quite this way, you know, but I mean that was a real problem, and I see the same problem. Well, well, I have this, I don't want to talk too much, but I've had this, I have imaginative pro had a situation just recently where I was shut off with the internet.\"}]},{\"id\":\"935e5fd7-b5cb-4551-82e8-f03385a85808\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Uh, basically, I was asked to put it, to identify myself and get, put in a certain number and then get a code. It wouldn't send me a code. I looked up. It says you may not get a code if you, your pattern of use has changed. Hm. Hm. And, well, it said, because, uh, you know, and I was thinking I must have done something that told the robot, you know, that I should,\"}]},{\"id\":\"0414d4ae-d5db-405f-af35-a22cdd8f8ba8\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"that maybe that I wasn't me. It's\"}]},{\"id\":\"85a756e3-d9ef-41f1-ae45-f3d7d9cee6ac\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"all those porn sites you've been going to, Gordon, I'm sure. And\"}]},{\"id\":\"539668df-ab61-4323-ad00-60befe620c84\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"so, but that's the problem, but I, to me, that's kind of an analogy with the ad writing. Um-hum, you know, you use a formula and it's not always right. Yeah. Did\"}]},{\"id\":\"8c166548-23ae-43e6-b869-cba00077184b\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"you pay your internet bill?\"}]},{\"id\":\"57dd24a2-b06a-479b-8012-44acbc30de1a\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, yeah, that's a question too. Yeah, I. Yeah. I made sure. Oh, that. But, but, but. And the thing is I tried, I couldn't find a person to talk to about it. Yes.\"}]},{\"id\":\"ff03a22c-a946-4e45-b01b-491bf3e395b7\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"That's, you know. Yeah, that's the\"}]},{\"id\":\"cbe755f7-11fc-4db7-9e00-ba97998ca61a\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"other thing, yeah. No. I want to tell you, so Papa Murphy's, it tells me I have an account, but I don't know my password. So, if I hit this thing, it's going to send it. It never sends me the numbers. So, I'm with you, I don't know why Papa Murphy's is mad at me, but evident,\"}]},{\"id\":\"c15f1107-c685-4ce0-a266-5544331c7d59\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So,\"}]},{\"id\":\"72dcc03a-12d4-447b-ab5b-32875cb8b4e9\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"if you can figure that out, please tell me because I just have quit being able to order online. I just call the person. Sure. Yeah, because it's easier because I don't ever get the link.\"}]},{\"id\":\"85ecf505-ee82-41f4-97d7-5d826ac51395\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And soon Papa Murphy's doesn't recognize your face?\"}]},{\"id\":\"b85dd7f4-499c-4612-a1b8-c50ca2920f7c\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I don't know. I don't know.\"}]},{\"id\":\"cfd32476-f96f-4809-b555-c48a73c68018\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"That's another access\"}]},{\"id\":\"40735462-04ff-455a-8c73-9955cb3fbd57\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"point. Yeah.\"}]},{\"id\":\"c1dcef2d-c652-4798-bc95-6071892b750c\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I don't know. Whatever it is, they don't like me and they won't send me the link, but I do have an account. Right. Yeah. I'm not sure how that works. So, I just want to say, I get it. Yeah. I've been there, done that. And you get so frustrated. Yeah, when the machine decides. So, you just want to do something really fast and get it done. Um-hum. And then,\"}]},{\"id\":\"c0c4fe09-7e51-4505-8533-bd697b1063fc\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"yeah. Yeah.\"}]},{\"id\":\"fd16c1af-ce36-4708-a098-d0a7efebdab8\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So what, what areas come to mind for you?\"}]},{\"id\":\"bbcdcb68-ebb8-45ef-a6ed-a158301cc316\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, we're we're we're talking about commerce here.\"}]},{\"id\":\"65a73cbd-74f1-4b67-b98c-e5560a4db717\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I is that covered?\"}]},{\"id\":\"e08a3b02-2fa0-40b3-b2d0-6699115525b2\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"The list or is that an additional\"}]},{\"id\":\"9e754643-f151-4ada-a52b-e17973596403\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"that might be an another thing you're talking about the the access or you know changing the way commerce interactions take place.\"}]},{\"id\":\"4417c478-1c43-4fe9-ae73-3eaa5d2ffcb5\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah, who has access and who doesn't? How is that getting decided? Yep.\"}]},{\"id\":\"4e620a20-b5c2-418c-9df3-73e8e4482441\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"You know, computers run on bits. They're either on or off. You know, zeros and ones. That's all computers are. That's all they've ever been and maybe all they'll ever be. I don't know what, what, what I'm thinking is, uh, let, let's say, uh, someone has some mental issues, maybe.\"}]},{\"id\":\"9bfe54b9-8a34-4b89-9c95-1b38845de660\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"How in the world would artificial intelligence analyze that? It seems to me there's a human element that someone who is trained and educated and experienced can talk to an individual maybe over a period of weeks or months and say, OK, you've got this issue or that issue, and everybody's a little different and they can fashion a way forward.\"}]},{\"id\":\"e2e405ca-6fc4-4a35-b8ce-57615cdf2cf9\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Um, how does a machine ever do that? Because they're, they're again, they're off and on, uh, they're zeros and ones, you know, they may have a collection of everything the human race has ever done, but how do you, how do you get it that focus? That's where I, I can't get my head around that one.\"}]},{\"id\":\"46b7c67b-44ab-49fb-9a26-5142c4de97d0\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, I, I don't know how the, the technology works, but one of the, the things related to those zeros and ones that AI is particularly good at is pattern recognition. And so it can be good. And in fact there are, are cases in the mental health field where by\"}]},{\"id\":\"f0808c43-d854-481f-8560-4543018c6780\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Monitoring by having AI have interactions, you know, you're doing your chat GPT conversations or whatever, it can notice when um\"}]},{\"id\":\"427aa414-921d-4a73-854e-7ee89839423b\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"People who are bipolar, for example, are going into a manic episode or are going into a depressive episode and potentially could then flag someone to get them help.\"}]},{\"id\":\"cd3fc493-122f-4c28-9ff5-cb276d0db615\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Or, you know, how many times do you hear about somebody who has committed suicide and the people that they live with say, well, you know, we knew they, they were having a hard time, but we had no idea it was that, that bad or that dire. And, um, so it's the, the pattern recognition.\"}]},{\"id\":\"6125c6f7-16cf-436b-a50d-b77d9fb8d748\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Um, that goes into that. Is that a substitute for all human interaction? Absolutely not, you know, is that a substitute for, for therapy and, and whatever? Absolutely not. But it can be a, a tool.\"}]},{\"id\":\"20a16231-e158-4eb5-9a4d-b2adf7f6d41e\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Does anyone, I am just going to jump in here. Does anyone have any sort of hesitancy about personal privacy with this? and I'd be interested to know other people's opinions. I do not use Facebook and I just have, or any sort of social media. I just have philosophical arguments against it for a lot of reasons, but\"}]},{\"id\":\"978ec0f8-bb4d-4a25-a032-b4abd2a5da09\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"There are things that I apparently do use that are AI and so.\"}]},{\"id\":\"2d3c313d-596f-4fad-ba11-e73af9c1652e\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"If I go onto Google Maps,\"}]},{\"id\":\"a9dadf58-07af-429a-a904-114b45aee89c\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Who sees that I'm doing that, you see what I mean? I'm just bringing up the subject because\"}]},{\"id\":\"a9a855be-ad2f-4750-84b6-f1b962a8db89\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"You know, when I was in high school and I read about Big Brother and George Orwell's 1984, it was just so far in the future. Well, here we're way past that, and I'm just curious. I mean, this is a, this is what I, this is one aspect of this that I've thought about, and I'd like to hear what other people think\"}]},{\"id\":\"4b532e3c-d4e1-484f-8328-53fbad0c4ec2\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"about that.\"}]},{\"id\":\"12cbc8d3-584e-4d9a-8b11-85c9294a7c09\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, Google knows when you use Google Maps. They, yes. And.\"}]},{\"id\":\"9fb79d97-8b98-495f-8d03-b9f804f0e64d\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"But they also know, so, you look up that you're going to buy a, oh, yeah. T-shirt. Let's say you're just going to buy a t-shirt and then all of a sudden you have all these ads on Ishirt. And you're thinking,\"}]},{\"id\":\"d64b5194-b9f4-4c9a-9585-cdde2666bc8d\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"and I have. Yeah. A plethora\"}]},{\"id\":\"63ca4911-9d20-4d57-833e-a8280d122950\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"of T-shirt ads I, I agree. Coming up when I'm\"}]},{\"id\":\"341fc77f-7849-4901-8ab5-4ef584f7aac9\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"trying to study something else. Yeah.\"}]},{\"id\":\"f7668b7a-b3d8-4d93-b955-42b9a44a82f5\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"That's my, that's my concern.\"}]},{\"id\":\"fae41c04-1847-4f29-99b0-118aaa1b5a05\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"We haven't even looked up stuff. We've been discussing stuff.\"}]},{\"id\":\"9878fab1-5a2d-4844-8823-6ea5b7a367d5\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yes. That will come up. I think Alexa, uh. Oh, yes, I think Alexa, I, I've, I, I firmly believe because you are right. You can just have, have coffee and talk about something and all of a sudden you have 50 ads. Yeah. Yeah. So, I've narrowed it down to Alexa. Is who I think it is. But I do like when she does. Well, you don't have Alexa. We don't have\"}]},{\"id\":\"68aae52c-dba6-420b-8a41-3a6d3a6eecbb\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Alexa. We don't have our phones. No. No. We were talking about. We were talking about a few, several different times over the last. Oh, yeah yeah. years and suddenly within two\"}]},{\"id\":\"7aa70792-ad04-48a0-b542-4e577799e941\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"hours,\"}]},{\"id\":\"14bb46e1-81f8-4b4b-bfde-0dba28194e4c\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"You mean you\"}]},{\"id\":\"3bff36d3-0278-496f-