\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Look how many phones are sitting out here. They're listening to us and recording all\"}]},{\"id\":\"27173e0e-751d-4d68-8f8a-c28cfef82faa\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"of this. Yeah, well, but keep in mind there's not a someone who cares. It's not a, it's not a person they're saying, Oh, Susie's doing.\"}]},{\"id\":\"122fe22e-a225-484c-b51c-da13b3b92837\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"In this right, it's, it's the, the pattern matching. It's the algorithm that that word scares me\"}]},{\"id\":\"998385a5-d1e8-4e13-9d16-98b42d0f6422\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"really bad, the algorithm. That's\"}]},{\"id\":\"23177a20-d035-4d1d-9735-05f5ce212598\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"all algorithm is, is a formula. No, I know what\"}]},{\"id\":\"3a9a0b39-4765-4671-ae69-1994809dde94\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"it is, but it's that what it does. Yes,\"}]},{\"id\":\"89ed6f83-01cb-4b1e-8916-727d3b72f577\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"yeah, and I think for me that's that access to accurate information, um, because when chat GPT first came out, that's when I saw a story about some pastors using it to write.\"}]},{\"id\":\"e5e60a7b-5580-4b25-b6c1-30515851169a\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And that for me was the question, where's that spiritual component? Where's that organic component, um, but it got me thinking about the algorithms that what if the algorithms become so overbearing, and maybe that's not the right word, but with all, they all put you in one little pigeon hole.\"}]},{\"id\":\"318ec692-4389-46ca-afb3-bba893b42764\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And when you want to step out, they say, well, no, you can't order Papa Murphy's pizza anymore.\"}]},{\"id\":\"ecf5fb44-8dc9-46e0-9807-dd0b4b67a989\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah. That's where\"}]},{\"id\":\"4aec2bbe-efff-4c4b-8bb5-202780b622f7\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I\"}]},{\"id\":\"95bb3f5c-965f-4833-ac1a-88df4f314ea7\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"am. I mean,\"}]},{\"id\":\"2e16fd5f-3fb5-4ad1-bdb4-5174d7ff5218\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I mean I\"}]},{\"id\":\"49afdb94-0a2a-4179-ac7f-e2b12f096edf\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"got, you ordered the wrong I got voted off the island. Yeah. You got voted off the\"}]},{\"id\":\"6fbc951b-ebbf-42ba-b1b6-fd592b21bffb\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"algorithm at. Do you have a nutritionist app? Maybe. Yeah, there you go.\"}]},{\"id\":\"eeea2052-0844-4ecd-8c4c-ffd60aa1abe9\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Voted off the island is what I call it. Yeah.\"}]},{\"id\":\"087cc7c4-7561-40a9-aa0d-47849e55dfef\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah. But you know somebody. You can talk to them on\"}]},{\"id\":\"186eb3ff-f615-482b-98e5-fb38e4da0a49\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"the phone. Uh, yeah, I can still call them now when they quit answering.\"}]},{\"id\":\"89d5fe5c-cf6e-4884-ac44-926123a938b8\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah I am definitely off the island.\"}]},{\"id\":\"fa12a44f-d542-4c82-bd05-c648d9a896f5\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah. Yeah. But I do wonder if any of that you\"}]},{\"id\":\"0c25b594-a9af-4493-88d1-5fde6c8d79d1\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"have, uh, put your name, your own name in Google. Say, you know. Oh, Google, find below again and see what comes up. Have you done that? Sure, no, I haven't. Not recently. You've got to do it. And my guess is you all have, we all have 2 or 3 or 5 pages, and some of, some of them very, very accurate, and some of it is just, who knows what.\"}]},{\"id\":\"738b0199-eb0f-4873-b70f-fe50e5fb7883\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I mean, it's something I think you should do that every, every so often. I think I would be afraid. Yes, I\"}]},{\"id\":\"7d2699d2-1919-4196-af78-9bba6f414392\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I don't want to know what they know. I don't know. I mean, a lot of it's innocuous. So, you know, I was on the school board, so my name was on every agenda of the school board. So if you Google me, you'll find a bunch of school board agendas. OK. That's public information. It has nothing to do with AI. It has.\"}]},{\"id\":\"533c8f8c-17f6-4552-9b5c-50634b333d4d\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Nothing to do with my privacy. I didn't, I don't get to the school district and the state requires it it's public information. OK,\"}]},{\"id\":\"d2bdd5d3-6603-4d1f-b504-df96226d499e\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"so you're transparent saying\"}]},{\"id\":\"4d0e2f8d-2b73-46f5-a89f-af89260dba69\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"that was data entry done.\"}]},{\"id\":\"ccdca45b-085b-414a-9804-9abcb5d9a8e4\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, it's a document that's the public, and my name just happens to be a word on the document, but and, and that's pre-AI, you know,\"}]},{\"id\":\"fcf9e655-6ef3-4768-b822-3707c9e48f6b\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"so just kind of real quick.\"}]},{\"id\":\"a235894b-0afc-49ca-bfcf-25d9c576bc80\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"You know, we're talking about, we know what it's like to have interpersonal communication.\"}]},{\"id\":\"036b7efd-ce57-4af7-9be6-cafa5664b4f0\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I'm 67. I won't ask, but I gotta think that we're looking at a lot of AI users who are two generations behind us and who just came from COVID.\"}]},{\"id\":\"6163f436-63a0-48ed-a79f-8e88a8da7f50\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Right. And they don't have.\"}]},{\"id\":\"0215d702-ec95-4801-96b7-46079de3a549\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"An appreciation or an understanding about the interpersonal. And so when they're siloed up in these AI chambers, and they're just getting hearing more and more of those algorithms, feeding them more what they wanna hear.\"}]},{\"id\":\"fe18fe61-00d1-4990-b339-51432384421e\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I think for me, that's, maybe that's a little, again, getting back to the macro level, but what does this look for? What does this do for Crook County?\"}]},{\"id\":\"863e433b-0d5f-4c04-a64a-eac5a69591e2\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"In the next decade or two decades is how we get along and or how we say, you know, I don't see it that way and I'm just gonna call you out on social media and the algorithms are gonna tell me how to psychologically observe you\"}]},{\"id\":\"92e6e40f-2cd2-41be-a9fd-ab689badc344\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"bless you,\"}]},{\"id\":\"0018f32e-1d21-47d1-82c0-306e725892c2\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"yeah, although\"}]},{\"id\":\"c3c17403-d572-4838-8b8c-d5225c886908\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So this isn't about what I think, but I do wonder, like with the, the pastors, um, using AI to create their sermons, is the problem that AI can write sermons, or is the problem that pastors choose to\"}]},{\"id\":\"7bd2ab29-6d90-45e1-a76a-37848553e961\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"You know, to not, to not do it. And I mean the same with all of the interactions, you know, we are.\"}]},{\"id\":\"89a27c02-2d5d-43f9-818c-51c605d2b30b\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Still in control, right? We can choose whether we use it or not. We can use what can control what we use it for. We can control that, you know, if we use it to, to give us a draft of something that we read it and write it and edit it and use those, those skills, um, you know, we're not at the point yet, maybe we'll get there, where AI decides.\"}]},{\"id\":\"9fa5a3a4-ca60-4b7c-961b-b450c85348e4\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"You know, you're not going to talk to Mark, you're going to talk to me, damn it, you know, and you're not going to have those interactions, you know, we, I think we have to hold on to our humanity in the face of this.\"}]},{\"id\":\"2cfef53a-d2dc-4b23-8a23-6b7e082343bd\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Right, so for every sermon I wrote, I shared some other even subconsciously. So when you talk about at a funeral, I'm sharing something about me. I can't help it. When you talk about writing, I think it gives the audience insights into that individual. Of course\"}]},{\"id\":\"84c8f076-14f1-41a2-8f6a-dc4f81e99054\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"it does.\"}]},{\"id\":\"6ec677ea-42d9-4bee-8fcc-23763b0e8dcb\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Because you can't help but share part of you. Right. And that's, that's, that's what makes it Person. Well, and,\"}]},{\"id\":\"17d0e6d3-d72a-465d-9010-705b20662f16\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"yes. Yeah.\"}]},{\"id\":\"98789a4c-2281-48de-a946-c485f55c7ee2\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"But when it makes it human.\"}]},{\"id\":\"15ed5e78-566e-4669-9350-62c8abd8cf70\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"But then what, but again, we have an appreciation for them because we know the inner person.\"}]},{\"id\":\"8c5e7790-6f38-4553-87bc-ff077fe79345\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I think.\"}]},{\"id\":\"aea29019-aab4-4d23-9f3c-7455cd957507\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, it's interesting you were talking about the youth, you know, some generations behind us, they don't have the life experiences that we've already had, so they, they can't understand it.\"}]},{\"id\":\"a8b0b2cf-d3bb-44a3-9e73-65ecb0f74b27\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And a lot of times when you, when you're growing up anyway, you know, oh, that's what my mom meant, or now I get it, but anyway, with, with them just learning through machines, you're not getting that personal human touch.\"}]},{\"id\":\"47755f72-e9f8-4185-91c7-9e1d77639a29\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, I, I agree, but we control that.\"}]},{\"id\":\"8a6cd2d3-c130-40ee-840f-f7edc7d45067\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Right, our children, I mean, if we're allowing our kids to be on the phone all the time or whatever, not paying\"}]},{\"id\":\"52b9486b-bbce-4db9-8cb2-87ed98c74b0e\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"attention,\"}]},{\"id\":\"ce00f4d8-2d06-44df-9e33-8809fbcbc57f\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"right, but we are allowed, you know, there's still a human piece, you know, you were talking about the conversation at the airport.\"}]},{\"id\":\"784a9b93-6646-4cb0-9d69-cab690152009\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And you know, the reason you used to have a conversation at the airport is because you were bored. You had time to kill, and there was nothing else to do, right? Now you pull out your phone because there is something to do. So in that sense, technology has\"}]},{\"id\":\"2365b1cf-aa4f-4d79-82d8-83158864ed6d\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Created an alternative. It's the same thing with AI. You know, you can write your own sermons from scratch or you can have AI generated, but you make that\"}]},{\"id\":\"c2854fed-e80c-4250-b32c-6f6b7cfcd869\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"decision. one thing on the phone, at least that's.\"}]},{\"id\":\"b7939256-76ff-4915-885e-56b1012ff931\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Real person.\"}]},{\"id\":\"0cd41323-b0ec-42cc-9eb7-9e77726c49a4\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"If they're talking on the phone. But all of the times they're not talking on the phone. Oh. They're texting or they're playing a game. Yeah.\"}]},{\"id\":\"a1323ebf-2817-4220-8b30-37489a85bbf2\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Or watching something else. Well, even if you're texting, I mean, you're usually texting to somebody else. I mean, so. It's still different, though. It is different, I know. But I mean. Yeah.\"}]},{\"id\":\"9b2e69fc-6653-4bb8-84b3-e4177ca51704\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So. Yeah. So, my daughter wanted to go to this small private college. It was very, very hard to get into.\"}]},{\"id\":\"39ad2083-8c18-4f72-97b2-64fa4c3402c2\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And she was 3rd in her class, and the valedictorian was obviously 1st in the class, and Ann got in the valedictorian didn't. So in the 2nd year, knowing the basketball coach because my daughter played basketball, I said why did Erica not get in.\"}]},{\"id\":\"6c12eca4-d9a7-418c-a0d7-212c5e35b19e\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And Ann did, and she said, you haven't figured that out, Susie, and I said, no. She said, that's because your daughter was the captain of the volleyball team, the captain of the basketball team, the track star. She took people and led them to a common goal. The valedictorian was a cross country runner. The only one that she motivated was herself.\"}]},{\"id\":\"fc4e716f-77e0-4c74-b660-15eeb0fe927e\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And we will always look towards the ends who take people towards a common goal. And I, I, I felt that was very that really made me think about it. And so you have like a Bill Gates who maybe sits there and is brilliant and does all of this, but then you have the person that can go out and get a group of people to move towards that common goal. And if we lose that, which I worry because of the children.\"}]},{\"id\":\"636d605c-1716-43f0-a0c7-a9aeac1266ec\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Of the dependence on TikTok and all of that and also the cruelty. I don't remember going to school with bullies. I don't remember that. That's very scary to me now with social media, they say such cruel things, and I have a granddaughter who in 8th grade kind of got in the mean girl thing and came to us and said, I don't like this. They want me to text this other little girl something.\"}]},{\"id\":\"a2ea1236-f20f-4175-8278-8d1ccd7f6ada\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And we talked to her about it, and we, we approached it and we got it handled, but how many of these children don't go to a parent or another authority.\"}]},{\"id\":\"1ab7e84b-20c6-4c77-878c-53a4fb5f19dd\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And, and it really, it's, it's scary that bullying in schools is going on to the extent that it is. And I, I, I think that they've lost, this isn't a person, this isn't two eyes looking at you, because how hard is it to confront people? It's very hard to confront people. We've all been uncomfortable when we've had to confront people, but if I can do it on this phone.\"}]},{\"id\":\"937a7da7-687e-4409-a1ab-6651a814023a\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Right. Heck, I have no. There's no interpersonal. It's just. No, no, no, and I think we have really lost. I, I worry about that. Particularly, like you say, the bullying increasing.\"}]},{\"id\":\"cfd2959a-716c-4374-b6e1-7d0ea8883176\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, there was a lot of bullying when I went to\"}]},{\"id\":\"385b59ae-4a10-44ce-a8e3-0004ee5c4489\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"school. Yeah. Well, I'm sorry. I must have been at a happy school. Then you\"}]},{\"id\":\"905e5331-c2b7-4ae4-8589-7cfcc0efc252\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"must have been. I was more physical. Or you were one of the cool\"}]},{\"id\":\"68259973-9373-484b-8d2e-5593350d88f5\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"kids. I've had, you know, I've thought that, uh, now, you know, I'd rather be a kid now, because if somebody tries to bully me, I can probably say something that'll demolish you. Take him down. Cause I don't have to worry about him punching\"}]},{\"id\":\"c4139a79-9fa0-4a1a-83df-ea5e72727a82\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"me.\"}]},{\"id\":\"6ca44884-24e7-450d-bea1-dd68952664f7\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, there's another thing. There's a different way of looking at it than the way I, but again, like I say, the bullying thing just is,\"}]},{\"id\":\"96b1dea2-ea52-4df1-a8f1-2ad0c06fc43b\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"and\"}]},{\"id\":\"da74abc2-8e8b-477e-ac5d-65037d3ce73c\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"let's lose sight of the audience because when I went to high school, graduated in '76, bullying, if it really got to what was settled behind the bleachers, you don't like to see it, but maybe a dozen people knew about it.\"}]},{\"id\":\"f154988f-ea6f-4873-909a-85d763cee157\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"With social media, by the time they get shared and reshared, it's thousands and thousands of people that are seeing a picture of you at your least flattering point. I mean, the graph, the depth of it is just frightening.\"}]},{\"id\":\"2abdfa0b-443c-45ab-9a7c-97c06a454e9d\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So,\"}]},{\"id\":\"84c60e79-92a1-42ba-8fa5-7b0ddd2f005c\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"yep.\"}]},{\"id\":\"bf0a9f11-ff2f-4f5b-8585-67ef66020d6d\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Agreed. But again, it's a generational difference. Yeah. Even with the, what bullying looks\"}]},{\"id\":\"7a21b5d1-d381-4427-b429-5c03413f0142\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"like, I think. I wonder what our parents would say about, you know what I mean? Yeah. That they probably.\"}]},{\"id\":\"3a656628-2c0d-41fe-b0c7-504d23ce0860\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, my mom was the one who introduced me to the concept of future shock, which is that events advance so quickly that the human really can't.\"}]},{\"id\":\"08c4a67e-1007-443a-9e3f-5a37437edafa\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Keep it going. Keep it going. It's like from the 60s, I think, 60s\"}]},{\"id\":\"625d600c-46d9-40ec-9757-ee529b0d5447\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"or 7. Yeah, Alvin Toffler wrote the book.\"}]},{\"id\":\"1496fbab-861b-4678-be86-a50185ccfa65\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So anyway, sorry. All right, I'll back\"}]},{\"id\":\"df3e5fdf-cd69-46a3-9afa-9aaeaf32f3b3\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"down. We're, we're, we're now.\"}]},{\"id\":\"bb8d3224-fe20-47f1-9d5b-ceb2425b9095\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"They're all, it's all good fodder for the for the discussion.\"}]},{\"id\":\"25139da4-bd95-4292-91b6-bfca6b2f96f5\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So let's bring the the AI.\"}]},{\"id\":\"a911c6bc-8039-45bc-a86f-79447400dcd4\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Discussion local, OK. How\"}]},{\"id\":\"a72f2187-8dbe-4839-b378-9d9d6dd0c5ac\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Would we anticipate AI coming up in Prineville? You know, I guess like the um\"}]},{\"id\":\"ea068252-2a19-40aa-94c8-3508b8f3bb79\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"The traffic cameras, we could decide that there was a need for traffic cameras and, you know, maybe we use AI for tracking that um in our local schools. um What,\"}]},{\"id\":\"dd44ad2f-b011-4f90-940a-3c5409101c7a\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"what are they teaching now? Do you know the curriculum there at\"}]},{\"id\":\"b87203a6-8c2f-4af6-9b72-cc46563f70dc\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"all?\"}]},{\"id\":\"16ca0a92-abc0-411e-a912-0bf38d6e7e07\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Um,\"}]},{\"id\":\"b65a45e7-6ac1-495e-8aed-3a29ad9bec21\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"For computer science when I was in high school many years ago, uh, typing, I learned to type. the most useful skill I've ever learned. I can type 100 words a minute right now. Um, so what, what are they teaching kids about this kind of stuff, you know, and maybe even 6th grade and on,\"}]},{\"id\":\"51603447-a440-407d-b763-73dce63f7a2c\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"you know, on a day to day basis, I don't know. I know our school district, in fact, I met with the superintendent yesterday, um, wants to.\"}]},{\"id\":\"e6ed0272-9bf1-42d6-913e-4417874e36b4\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Be a leader in using and managing it. Um, they have an AI committee that includes staff and parents and students, you know, who are having these conversations internally. Um, I haven't personally seen any policies or anything that have come out, but I know that's\"}]},{\"id\":\"d5ba3064-ae94-4957-a499-9ab2dcd96bb8\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"In the works. So they don't have a no AI anywhere, nor do they have a, you know, throw out all the teachers and just sit behind your computer. So, um, all of our students from\"}]},{\"id\":\"682ae6ee-8325-40b3-9035-cc0d252d1dd4\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"6th grade on have um access to their own computing device, um, and they get used in different classes to different degrees.\"}]},{\"id\":\"2a40c6c0-1207-4c96-bd09-0508af8d066c\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Um, the state, um,\"}]},{\"id\":\"8aab1a9a-e20b-4687-b758-507db9b67dbc\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Implemented a mandate, no phones during the school day mandate this past year. Um, and, you know, it, it's too new to see what what the impact has been. In fact, I recently read an article that said that the first year of a phone ban.\"}]},{\"id\":\"ec27497e-caaa-4384-bb7e-778717030504\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"It is ugly just because there's implementation challenges and stuff, you know, you have to kind of get in that habit for 2 or 3 years before you can really see it in terms of student performance or behavior or anything like that. So we'll we'll see where that goes.\"}]},{\"id\":\"120c4e55-0f9b-4dcc-bc02-2cab959b4b58\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Um,\"}]},{\"id\":\"17306c3a-3cdc-4105-9ba8-50f09fad23a4\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Where does critical thinking come into that, though? I mean, to teach kids to think apart from AI or how to channel AI.\"}]},{\"id\":\"affead67-6ed5-4ae9-9aee-1d96950f25fb\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, I mean, critical thinking would come.\"}]},{\"id\":\"ba8d07f3-7f36-4d64-a006-30e6eddd27e3\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"In every class, at least in theory, right? Um, that that's the, the plan. There is not\"}]},{\"id\":\"0b84fcab-702c-4153-918a-e739a64365d3\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"To the best of my knowledge, a\"}]},{\"id\":\"aa5cd789-6218-41a6-a34d-6ec1dad540d3\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Computer class that everybody takes. You know, there's a robotics class and there's a coding class, and you know there are technology classes that are available, but it's not like, you know, typing or whatever where just everybody learns it, you know. Back when my daughter was in school 15 years ago.\"}]},{\"id\":\"cff1941e-5a32-4011-9e32-148c7bcfee28\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Um, before they all got the one on one computers, they did, you know, every student had a keyboarding section, right? They didn't have typewriters, but, you know, they at least went and learned keyboarding. Um, I don't think they do that anymore.\"}]},{\"id\":\"6788e488-c2cc-4e9f-8c62-704cf864f66f\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Um, I haven't seen that in the schools in a while, but, um,\"}]},{\"id\":\"7b3288d9-4fd4-4a12-8cef-6ae4a8f09ed3\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"but what's the, the argument, people, you said people are mixed, you know, not maybe not fifty-fifty, but a lot of people don't like this. What's their rationale for not liking it?\"}]},{\"id\":\"abc5d7e5-9c7f-4b40-97e6-46490e2b0d1b\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Or are they afraid of it? They don't understand it. I,\"}]},{\"id\":\"0e766213-68e8-43e7-b75c-9c8275dc2d10\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I would guess that that's it, because everyone is very afraid of what they don't understand. And that's also a good, a good thing for this conversation to increase our awareness and.\"}]},{\"id\":\"a93e4e98-9451-47b7-b997-f4db1a5557a6\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"What we know about this topic, so that we know more about it, so then we're not going to be afraid of it, but be able to, you know, make the decisions about how, how we're going to use this in our community.\"}]},{\"id\":\"7dd268ee-8351-4570-a9ef-f8bef08344fa\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"But I, I think your point is a good one cause that's always fear of something they don't understand is, is where that hard no usually comes from.\"}]},{\"id\":\"c7f7d56f-e102-47b4-bf41-c0e88141b591\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah, the change or I don't get to be in control of this, and I wonder how much that's even demographically. I mean, the old salesman in me is thinking, OK, for our age, hey, AI is here, and you know what, it's going to help diagnose your health issues that much faster and that much better. Well, who doesn't want to get behind that?\"}]},{\"id\":\"975d0245-621a-4367-a981-d41a04a10c51\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, I, I think it's part of the Papa Murphy's app.\"}]},{\"id\":\"30fbb331-58b3-4919-88b1-fac09d320075\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah, is that that\"}]},{\"id\":\"ad20cc2f-df4b-4d9d-bd2c-191f97dfc1ed\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"a\"}]},{\"id\":\"50aaa43c-99e0-43e9-9730-89379e3d6b62\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"lot\"}]},{\"id\":\"3a1719d1-5081-49d6-bae7-e4817088e25c\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"of I told that you guys have all united over Papa\"}]},{\"id\":\"8aea0f3c-3e78-41df-a9ae-840f9ac5c076\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Murphy's. Now we're gonna all just be sending you all gonna go to Papa Murphy's today.\"}]},{\"id\":\"3e852c4e-af2a-4f17-bcee-b8f20a3404d9\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I think that the salesman of it, you know, affects for whom. I mean, I think it depends on the demographics. It's going to be greater, you know, differences of different interests and different um.\"}]},{\"id\":\"903aa958-1002-4a5b-87c1-fc8ac6a1135b\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Interest in different fields and different amounts of interest.\"}]},{\"id\":\"ff25892a-1477-4aa5-a37c-d305ed43d1d0\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, and different priorities. So my daughter is 25, so she, you know, has grown up with computers and\"}]},{\"id\":\"5ea314b8-1f1f-44e8-a19b-92da427a98ec\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I am way more pro AI than she is. OK, what she.\"}]},{\"id\":\"70481745-f212-42b1-9755-6fb96dd4a398\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"What what comes into her world, and of course none of us get access to perfect information, right, is AI uses so much water, it uses so much electricity, it's bad for the environment.\"}]},{\"id\":\"e2fe3be0-f5c4-4510-895c-5982e8162f70\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And, you know, as a person of her generation, not that we don't care about the environment, but, you know, they are very sensitive to the environment. And so, um, Mike, to your point, it's, it's true that there is somewhat, somewhat of a generational component, there's somewhat of a political perspective component. There's an education level component, um.\"}]},{\"id\":\"b9cf4ab3-5ace-4d90-9c8f-751e3a78423f\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So, you know, the answer is lots of things.\"}]},{\"id\":\"e8fee126-7ca1-4840-a2bd-3a2a00fd42c7\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I think a big part of it, Margaret, is your point that it's still so big and we've heard about it for the last 2 or 3 years really intensely, but we're not seeing.\"}]},{\"id\":\"e90ecf64-7e15-4db3-82e5-5b99df6fca0b\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Actual tangible positives and actual tangible negatives. Right now, a lot of it's, oh, well, the robots are going to take over the world. Well, you know, it hasn't happened yet. Could it happen? Yeah, maybe. You know, um, we're not going to have any water.\"}]},{\"id\":\"2dc8f1c5-948d-4b2f-b0c3-6e0b6ca08302\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Electricity hasn't happened yet. Could it? Maybe. It's going to, you know, cure all medical problems. Well, it hasn't happened yet, but you know, it's making impacts. We just, it's so theoretical still that it's hyperbolic.\"}]},{\"id\":\"bbe967c4-efe9-4b3f-880e-bdc1440ae829\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And so people, you know, pick whatever is the most important thing, and, and that sets their mindset. And so that's why we're doing this, is to find out, you know, what are the things that that are setting your mindset today, and, you know, is it\"}]},{\"id\":\"01c82069-31ff-4d5d-a2e9-6739bbd5972f\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"time that just needs to happen till we all get more comfortable? Is it education? Is it, you know, you are\"}]},{\"id\":\"caf7fcd8-7510-4d32-ad29-f280268eba85\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Pro AI at the moment, but you know, the next time you go in and if you get a cancer diagnosis that was diagnosed early enough that they can treat it because the AI could read it better than a radiologist could, now you're really pro AI, right? Because it has a personal connection.\"}]},{\"id\":\"7625ed6b-568a-4361-b2d8-726384ea44e0\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Could have saved my, possibly could have saved my wife's life. Um-hum. Um-hum. And I mean, she died of cancer and we didn't catch it. It wasn't caught until too late to do anything. Yeah. I mean, I don't, you know, I don't, I'm not looking for sympathy or anything. I'm just pointing out that. Yeah. That, that's one thing I definitely would have wished that they had had more, you know. Um-hum. I think they were using some of it, you know, but it was not, you know.\"}]},{\"id\":\"c0c1bf0b-cb38-4af7-8f0a-0bdf2529fa24\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah, but that's one thing I'm in favor of.\"}]},{\"id\":\"1ed5cb1c-e974-404e-affd-ed99b9bb212a\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah, well, and, and even some of the, the negative things, you know, AI itself isn't.\"}]},{\"id\":\"76df5b00-1ad5-4236-a064-1d8865a69301\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"A water and power user data centers where AI is implemented are the water and power users, but AI has the capability to develop new technologies for managing water and power efficiency. AI to cure. Exactly, you know, so.\"}]},{\"id\":\"11f71e87-2720-4961-bb9d-38f89a9d58ec\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"But we haven't achieved any of that. We're not seeing a lot of tangible results right now. And so I think that's part of what makes it scary, you know, because the possibilities are huge\"}]},{\"id\":\"96a671f3-c8b8-41dc-8bd1-6a9a69299c11\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"and policy has not kept up with influence.\"}]},{\"id\":\"9cca66be-de19-4f73-b0af-70c50711c774\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Correct. And that's the challenge, you know, when the\"}]},{\"id\":\"d8768c1e-352f-4fc5-ad02-136956c02455\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Executives at the AI companies talk to Congress and say, please regulate us.\"}]},{\"id\":\"c1ea8119-865c-47af-a58a-07b9c46538fb\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I tend to listen, you know, but what I haven't seen is, please tell us we can't do this, or please tell us to do this, this, you know, we don't see the specifics, you know, just we need regulation. What is that? What\"}]},{\"id\":\"51180b74-e493-4f4c-8f06-d8eae0f5595a\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"does\"}]},{\"id\":\"21ee8c63-5c01-4e96-9c6d-c8141f12cbb6\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"that mean?\"}]},{\"id\":\"a1e04b29-0128-4d3f-a7ca-e7f4c103bda6\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"What's disallowed,\"}]},{\"id\":\"b89e18f8-9c58-452c-8099-d078dac4c0c8\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"right?\"}]},{\"id\":\"2abb70a7-d5c1-49f4-bade-8518b1721328\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So, um,\"}]},{\"id\":\"cda11a60-7bd8-49e9-9e1f-5cbfc0c4fd1d\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"At least to my mind, there's just a lot of open possibilities that that hyperbolize everything.\"}]},{\"id\":\"31396342-c615-4fa6-85e5-878a32a0d81f\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"But the bottom line is though, I think, well, I don't want to say the bottom line, but I think we should be talking about how do we use, how do we use it or not use it. Like one thing I'm interested in is whether we continue to have people answering the phone, or whether, you know,\"}]},{\"id\":\"5a34fad3-c6fd-40d5-9a49-76fa16171fa4\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And, of course, it's very frustrating to have a robot answering, you know. Well, and\"}]},{\"id\":\"9b96444e-217f-4e91-94cf-511980849852\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"eventually after three or four hours if they finally connect you to a person. Well,\"}]},{\"id\":\"5ef5458f-a927-4389-9515-e8732a53e86a\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"you learn techniques and you learn if you put, if, if you put the, push the right button and you, you know, make the right choice, you get sent to a person.\"}]},{\"id\":\"1c45b3fc-fd64-4c56-9956-9f176ca23e85\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"But then where are they getting their?\"}]},{\"id\":\"d4207000-740c-478d-a644-f4271173d84f\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, and that's it. You know, people aren't infallible either. You know, when you mentioned that early in my career, I used to run a tech support organization for a high tech company. So I had humans who worked for me, and when people had problems with our product, we would talk them through it.\"}]},{\"id\":\"7ac3b2ca-aa48-4040-8d89-c1b0a0c6bc69\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And if we hit a problem that we didn't know, we could walk across the building and talk to the engineer and, you know, get an answer. But I'm sure, even though all of my people were, of course, perfect, that there were still people who called and got a bad answer.\"}]},{\"id\":\"95479548-6c68-45a8-bbc2-fb9d9beb8cec\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And since then, you know, this was back in the 80s.\"}]},{\"id\":\"4aeb3599-1c8d-4853-804d-47e3d66caef1\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Now tech support has been offshored, right? So, and consolidated. So if you call for tech support, you still can talk to a human, but they have a script and they will take you through the script. They don't have access to the engineers. They don't actually use the product. They just have a script. So you're talking to a human.\"}]},{\"id\":\"2d2dc559-1a72-4a6c-b1d1-7800402f191c\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"But you're not necessarily\"}]},{\"id\":\"a29ced20-f35f-40df-bfce-148489462b63\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"getting\"}]},{\"id\":\"3179b3a7-d251-4170-be50-bd097d01b28c\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"the script provided by an algorithm of\"}]},{\"id\":\"a686605c-8e6e-41d3-9c0f-31bf0476f493\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"great information, right? At the same time, I will share, I have spent hours with my chatbot trying to solve technical problems, and it has taken me through the backwoods of Windows and not solved my problem.\"}]},{\"id\":\"213969a3-1614-4d6d-b85b-a7d029fddd1e\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Could I have gotten the problem solved with a human? Maybe. I don't know. So it's not necessarily the technology, other than it was maybe more work for me to type my conversations and then try stuff and whatnot. But bad information.\"}]},{\"id\":\"95a817f8-c7da-42b7-af1d-1d94a9a8b95c\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Coming from a chatbot and bad information coming from a human is still bad information.\"}]},{\"id\":\"ecd6a91f-2b7b-497d-beb4-f144667ed5e7\",\"interview\":\"spk_5\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, yeah, I have, I've put it this way, I have to talked to some pretty bad humans, and I've had some pretty bad humans worked on me. Some of them, their, their whole thing is to get the person off the phone as quick as possible so they can finish doing their, well, I, I don't want to say anything sexist, but I mean, you know,\"}]},{\"id\":\"e391a033-5066-4d77-887d-e6288044fafd\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"well.\"}]},{\"id\":\"e81c94b5-9bcc-44c1-90da-96ea629e578f\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"A whole deeper conversation, which we're not here to discuss is the incentives that we have in this world that lead things to go the way they are, right? When you're incentivized as a tech support person on how many calls you handle, you are actually incentivized to get people off the phone, not to solve their problem. Um, so, and you know, the same thing goes for.\"}]},{\"id\":\"ce32d365-acf3-4b17-a444-674dbc185129\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"tech billionaires, you know, what incentivizes them? The same thing goes for government officials. What incentivizes them to make the choices that they make.\"}]},{\"id\":\"8693dda4-2084-4850-93c8-4f371b82dec0\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So, we have run out of time and gotten completely off track, but that's OK.\"}]},{\"id\":\"e8817172-1168-415c-a207-8dba0c897854\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, I'm looking at that number 2, you know, the question of what are the risks that assumes, in my mind, it assumes that people are willing to take a risk, which means they're willing to at least explore rather than just say no.\"}]},{\"id\":\"4147f259-8420-4caa-b5a6-b34da4db21a5\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah, because if you say no, there's no risk, but if we all agree that AI is inevitable.\"}]},{\"id\":\"ba2859ba-95f7-437b-b849-4405ba6bf34f\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well,\"}]},{\"id\":\"f1dfc013-117a-46a2-b1a8-da305f9d2b5c\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"If you say no, you're not willing to take the risk.\"}]},{\"id\":\"583281ec-05cc-4144-a570-568da1587c0c\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"But if we assume that AI is inevitable, then risks will need to be taken.\"}]},{\"id\":\"f7dbfa06-bc4c-435f-836c-0907842c0981\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah, and I would posit that even if you say no, you're taking a risk of not being able to engage in some part of society or some part of the economy or however AI is, is working.\"}]},{\"id\":\"63c05571-17db-47a8-866d-77ef2d352d8f\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Right. You know, if Susie's not willing to take the risk to call for her pizza, she's not going to get pizza,\"}]},{\"id\":\"cc135990-967d-4e6c-b6e6-3fe5f3c3ccba\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"right?\"}]},{\"id\":\"19478a2f-8f93-4250-80cf-942a18b767ad\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, I'm looking at the risks of effect. I'm looking to the question, what effects do we want AI to have on our community? What are the risks? And if you're just going to say no, it tells me that you're not willing to take a risk. If you accept that AI is inevitable.\"}]},{\"id\":\"14c56d9c-5448-4fb5-b499-af48c27db693\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well then we're gonna have to figure out how to manage them and then we get back to effects for whom and on whom.\"}]},{\"id\":\"ca53b826-9120-4284-811e-5c217568dc68\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Which I'm happy to hear you're having community conversations with the marginalized folks because again AI in the information retrieval stage, a lot of it has been put in by white males, not all of it, but a lot of it, but there are a lot of other voices in our community.\"}]},{\"id\":\"daa88634-2925-4c26-99b3-865ff5653a03\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"What does that boil down to on the local level for people like Suzie and others who might be trying to figure out how to manage the AI and or use it for the benefit of all to make sure that you have all their voices.\"}]},{\"id\":\"b71b8991-b4bc-4d0a-8bef-bbb4e124bd06\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And the things we don't want to change.\"}]},{\"id\":\"0b45925d-25cc-401d-b07e-06b6da0fd285\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Changes are. Well, the human connection, we don't want to change. Right, right. Compassion.\"}]},{\"id\":\"0d35d096-5f1e-467d-bc7b-ab6144177341\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"We'll we'll put that on the absolutely keep list, right, is compassion and human\"}]},{\"id\":\"f5e2e2ec-fab3-4c79-8dda-1f508cf91db9\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"connection, or is it, or is it the other way? Is it how is it that we really double down on fostering interpersonal connections in a time of\"}]},{\"id\":\"dda46a8d-e511-4794-8572-dddb9800fd09\",\"interview\":\"spk_0\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"AI?\"}]},{\"id\":\"927b2912-c210-4fdb-b53b-aba4d2b75eba\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, and, and that's an important thing. Rather than trying to limit AI, maybe we need to kind of up our human game to balance it, right?\"}]},{\"id\":\"9271d153-4aa9-4eb9-bc64-59877779a4c9\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I'm done. Sorry, you're never done. I'm preaching. You are never done. I know.\"}]},{\"id\":\"882f5557-60e9-4165-8e0c-365e390d5598\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"OK, so this is just reporting back what we've been talking about as a group, so that's good.\"}]},{\"id\":\"0c15d335-b4f8-4b6b-9a74-4682a21486ea\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Um,\"}]},{\"id\":\"6089e133-d3c2-4e42-a343-b705d2cbc48f\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"So, thank you very much for your time and your engagement and your participation in the discussion. Um, if you haven't taken the poll, I would encourage you to take it, um, either the QR code on there or you can shoot the QR code off the the screen here if you want to do that. Um.\"}]},{\"id\":\"73cfd819-ac02-4c75-837a-47b9c3396d3f\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"If you have friends that you think might\"}]},{\"id\":\"56e71772-34fc-4685-8085-422d97cc8f6b\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Get value from these um kinds of discussions, point them to us. Probably the easiest way is to send them to the poll, which will link them to the communicate conversations. They can join the online ones. They can go up to Madras or Redmond or, or whatever to some of the other sessions if they'd like. Um, on the sign-in sheet, there was a place for you to put your email and, and note if you wanted to be.\"}]},{\"id\":\"6316f998-c57f-4564-b8aa-04e655665f5c\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"If you want to either help with this effort or just stay connected to it and we're happy to um\"}]},{\"id\":\"f07b4866-f0f1-4a61-8f04-44184030434c\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"To do that and, you know, give us any other suggestions or thoughts you have on ways that we can, can be gathering this information and engaging people in a\"}]},{\"id\":\"5ed4fc87-5180-435e-a51d-76b05871006b\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Honest and conversive way, in a human way, um.\"}]},{\"id\":\"65bc0fa1-2b6e-40cf-a89f-3fdb66abbb86\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"To try to make things better and\"}]},{\"id\":\"15a1f3cc-855c-44b3-a591-db525bce4956\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Give Suzie some guidance on\"}]},{\"id\":\"02b7effd-2bea-410e-b3b0-6f5618965e18\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"What the county or the school district or whoever should and shouldn't be doing with AI.\"}]},{\"id\":\"299a3811-947f-4018-b832-ba3af359e1ea\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Thank you for being.\"}]},{\"id\":\"2c753ce0-1a6d-425b-8cce-e0986e639f09\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Thank you for coming,\"}]},{\"id\":\"ade1946f-bc7f-4d18-b2d5-88c3c7d4f012\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"everyone. I really, it's, uh,\"}]},{\"id\":\"92d107bd-fbae-459b-bbd0-03f17c831b9c\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"this, this process, I can tell you from experience is, um, well worth the time and, and part of the experience.\"}]},{\"id\":\"efe7d08c-c7c5-4af4-a988-effcc5e0e113\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"For me was understanding that it still is we the people.\"}]},{\"id\":\"bd45deff-b9a4-4bd7-9d3b-679f961bbf27\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"If we sit down and talk to each other, you know, we can talk about being frustrated by the political process, and this is not a political forum at all. This is, uh, and my experience with the, the assembly is there's a lot part of it is large group and part of it is very small, and that's where the, the collaborative discussion really happens and.\"}]},{\"id\":\"36d2452e-11ba-4b00-b3d4-9ab3167cda3b\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"And, and I know this is kind of a trite thing, but we really do have more in common than we have differences.\"}]},{\"id\":\"65b4966b-7e03-4b69-97c8-55481725c114\",\"interview\":\"spk_3\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Anyway, that's my, my, uh, rah rah for the civic assembly process because it's, it was really an amazing experience.\"}]},{\"id\":\"fc0d05d8-73fb-44f6-a488-3d7e116a865d\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Well, I've always learned over the years that, uh, you can,\"}]},{\"id\":\"e06d5717-dd98-4943-8f5a-b495aaefeaec\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"You can make things happen or you can watch things happen or you can let them be happen to you and and complain all afternoon and and uh nothing much happens if you're sitting home and.\"}]},{\"id\":\"4d0781bc-0187-4742-91d6-30de18b457a9\",\"interview\":\"spk_4\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I'm not joining the party, so to speak. Yeah, yeah.\"}]},{\"id\":\"705a5fc4-c4c1-4922-b321-93ed48cbe43e\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Then you wonder what happened. I. You wonder what. Yeah. Right.\"}]},{\"id\":\"0349d84a-4371-406e-a48b-f09a5fa805aa\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah. Yeah.\"}]},{\"id\":\"b9df4a31-84c0-471f-a300-65f56ac2d036\",\"interview\":\"spk_2\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Very well\"}]},{\"id\":\"799db4a3-4eef-4df6-b6ca-37cb9dc226d9\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"said. Excellent. Well, again, thank you so much. OK. Everybody.\"}]},{\"id\":\"b86cd35d-05cd-402b-911d-d53fe010be61\",\"interview\":\"spk_7\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yeah.\"}]},{\"id\":\"d5a171d3-0b53-473f-9360-8bbd9e8fca9e\",\"interview\":\"spk_8\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"OK,\"}]},{\"id\":\"658ec669-c772-42e9-bdeb-42b1fe223748\",\"interview\":\"spk_6\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"I don't think the library.\"}]},{\"id\":\"0be70edd-ad02-4d9e-8758-2d6c04250658\",\"interview\":\"spk_1\",\"data\":[\"text\",{\"text\":\"Yes, thank you.\"}]}],\"date\":\"2026-06-23T07:38:32.902Z\"}],\"metadata\":[\"v0.2\",{\"duration\":0,\"startTimestamp\":1782200189990,\"totalCost\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"organization\":\"\"}]},\"analytics\":{\"totalDurationMs\":122910,\"totalTokens\":670400,\"totalCost\":1.7370349999999997,\"steps\":[{\"n